hadiths[331]{hadithnumber,text}:
6169,"Abu-Saleh samaan ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik baar aik shakhs rastey mein chala ja raha tha usko shadeed piyaas lagi , usey aik kunwaan mila wo us kuwein mein utra aur pani piya, phir wo kuwein se nikla to uske samney aik kutta zor-zor se haanp raha tha, piyaas ki wjah se keechad chaat raha tha, us shakhs ne (dil mein) kaha : ye kutta bhi piyaas se usi haalat ko pahuncha hai jo meri hui thi. wo kuwein mein utra aur apne mozey ko pani se bharaa phir usko munh se pakda yahan tak ke uper chadh aaya, phir us ne kuttey ko pani pilaya . Allah Taala ne usey us neki ka badla diya usko bakhsh diya. logon ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! hamarey liye un janwaron mein ajr hai? to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nami rakhney waley har jigar main ( kisi bhi jaandaar ka ho. ( ajr hai."
6170,"Hisham ne Muhammad (bin Sirin ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik faahisha aurat ne aik sakht garm din mein aik kutta dekha jo aik kuwein ke gird chakkar laga raha tha. piyaas ki wjah se us ne zaban bahar nikali hui thi us aurat ne uski khaatir apna moza utara (aur iske zariey pani nikal kar us kuttey ko pilaya ( to usko bakhsh diya gaya."
6171,"Hisham ne Muhammad (bin Sirin ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik faahisha aurat ne aik sakht garm din mein aik kutta dekha jo aik kuwein ke gird chakkar laga raha tha. piyaas ki wjah se us ne zaban bahar nikali hui thi us aurat ne uski khaatir apna moza utara (aur iske zariey pani nikal kar us kuttey ko pilaya ( to usko bakhsh diya gaya."
6172,"Ayub sakhtiyan ne Muhammad-bin Sirin se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik kutta aik ( gahrey , kachchey ( kuwein ke gird chakkar laga raha tha aur piyaas ki shiddat se marney ke qareeb tha ke Bani-Israeel ki faahisha aurton mein se aik faahisha ne usko dekha to usne apna mota moza utara aur uske zariey se us ( kuttey (ke liye pani nikala aur wo pani usey pilaya to is bina par usko bakhsh diya gaya."
6173,"Ayub sakhtiyan ne Muhammad-bin Sirin se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik kutta aik ( gahrey , kachchey ( kuwein ke gird chakkar laga raha tha aur piyaas ki shiddat se marney ke qareeb tha ke Bani-Israeel ki faahisha aurton mein se aik faahisha ne usko dekha to usne apna mota moza utara aur uske zariey se us ( kuttey (ke liye pani nikala aur wo pani usey pilaya to is bina par usko bakhsh diya gaya."
6174,"abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne bataya ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kehtey huey suna : Allah Taala farmata hai. ibne-Aadam dehar (waqt, zamaney) ko bura kehta hai jabke ( rab ( dehar main hi hun. raat aur din ( jinhein insan waqt kehta hai) mere hath mein hain."
6175,"abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne bataya ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kehtey huey suna : Allah Taala farmata hai. ibne-Aadam dehar (waqt, zamaney) ko bura kehta hai jabke ( rab ( dehar main hi hun. raat aur din ( jinhein insan waqt kehta hai) mere hath mein hain."
6176,"Sufiyan ne Zohri se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne ibne-Musaiyab se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala farmata hai. ibne-Aadam mujhey takleef deta hai (naraz karta hai) wo zamaney ko bura kehta hai jabke main hi (rab) dehar hun, raat aur din ko palat-ta hun."
6177,"Sufiyan ne Zohri se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne ibne-Musaiyab se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala farmata hai. ibne-Aadam mujhey takleef deta hai (naraz karta hai) wo zamaney ko bura kehta hai jabke main hi (rab) dehar hun, raat aur din ko palat-ta hun."
6178,"Mamar ne hamein Zohri se khabar di unhon-ne ibne-Musaiyab se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki : kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne irshad farmaya : ibne-Aadam mujhey taklif deta hai wo kehta hai. haaye zamaney ( waqt) ki naamuraadi! tum mein se koi haaye zamaney ki naamuraadi! ( jaisa jumla ( na kahey , kyonke dehar (ka Malik) main hun. raat aur din ko palat-ta hon aur main jab chaahunga unki bisaat lapet dunga."
6179,"Mamar ne hamein Zohri se khabar di unhon-ne ibne-Musaiyab se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki : kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne irshad farmaya : ibne-Aadam mujhey taklif deta hai wo kehta hai. haaye zamaney ( waqt) ki naamuraadi! tum mein se koi haaye zamaney ki naamuraadi! ( jaisa jumla ( na kahey , kyonke dehar (ka Malik) main hun. raat aur din ko palat-ta hon aur main jab chaahunga unki bisaat lapet dunga."
6180,Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs ye na kahey ke haaye zamaney ki naamuraadi! kyonke Allah Taala hi zamaney (ka Malik ( hai.
6181,Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs ye na kahey ke haaye zamaney ki naamuraadi! kyonke Allah Taala hi zamaney (ka Malik ( hai.
6182,"Ibne-Sirin ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : zamaney ko bura mat kaho kyonke Allah Taala hi zamana (ka Malik ( hai."
6183,"Ibne-Sirin ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : zamaney ko bura mat kaho kyonke Allah Taala hi zamana (ka Malik ( hai."
6184,"Ayub ne Ibne-Sirin se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs zamaney ko bura na kahey, kyonke Allah Taala hi zamaney (ka Malik) hai aur tum mein se koi shakhs inab ( angoor aur uski bail) ko karam na kahey, kyonke karam (asl) main musalman aadmi hota hai."
6185,"Ayub ne Ibne-Sirin se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs zamaney ko bura na kahey, kyonke Allah Taala hi zamaney (ka Malik) hai aur tum mein se koi shakhs inab ( angoor aur uski bail) ko karam na kahey, kyonke karam (asl) main musalman aadmi hota hai."
6186,"Saeed ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, ke aap ne farmaya : ( angoor aur uski bail ko) karam na kaho , kyonke (haqiqat mein) karam momin ka dil hota hai."
6187,"Saeed ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, ke aap ne farmaya : ( angoor aur uski bail ko) karam na kaho , kyonke (haqiqat mein) karam momin ka dil hota hai."
6188,"Hisham ne Ibne-Sirin se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki aap ne farmaya : (angoor aur uski bail) ko karam na kaho, kyonke karam (asl mein) musalman aadmi hota hai."
6189,"Hisham ne Ibne-Sirin se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki aap ne farmaya : (angoor aur uski bail) ko karam na kaho, kyonke karam (asl mein) musalman aadmi hota hai."
6190,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs (angoor aur uski bail ko) karam na kahey kyonke karam to momin ka dil hai."
6191,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs (angoor aur uski bail ko) karam na kahey kyonke karam to momin ka dil hai."
6192,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sunain . unhon-ne kai hadisein bayan kin unmein ye bhi thi : aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs angoor aur uski bail ko akaram na kahey , kyonke akaram to musalman aadmi hota hai."
6193,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sunain . unhon-ne kai hadisein bayan kin unmein ye bhi thi : aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs angoor aur uski bail ko akaram na kahey , kyonke akaram to musalman aadmi hota hai."
6194,"Isa-bin-Yonus ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Samak-bin-Harab se, unhon-ne Alqama-bin-Waail se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : (angoor aur uski bail ko) akaram na kaha karo. lekin habla keh lo. aap ki murad angoor se thi."
6195,"Isa-bin-Yonus ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Samak-bin-Harab se, unhon-ne Alqama-bin-Waail se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : (angoor aur uski bail ko) akaram na kaha karo. lekin habla keh lo. aap ki murad angoor se thi."
6196,"Usman-bin-Umar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Samak se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Alqama-bin-Waail se suna, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, ke aap ne farmaya : akaram na kaho lekin angoor aur habla, (angoor ki bail) keh lo."
6197,"Usman-bin-Umar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Samak se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Alqama-bin-Waail se suna, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, ke aap ne farmaya : akaram na kaho lekin angoor aur habla, (angoor ki bail) keh lo."
6198,"Alaa ke walid ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs (kisi ko) mera banda aur meri bandi na kahey , tum sab Allah ke bandey ho aur tumhari tamam auratein Allah ki bandiyaan hain. albatta yun keh sakta hai. mera ladka meri ladki , mera jawan , khaadim , meri khaadima."
6199,"Alaa ke walid ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs (kisi ko) mera banda aur meri bandi na kahey , tum sab Allah ke bandey ho aur tumhari tamam auratein Allah ki bandiyaan hain. albatta yun keh sakta hai. mera ladka meri ladki , mera jawan , khaadim , meri khaadima."
6200,"Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs (kisi ghulam ko) mera banda na kahey , to tum sab Allah ke bandey ho, albatta ye keh sakta hai: mera jawan, aur na ghulam ye kahey : mera rab (paalne wala) albatta mera saiyyed ( aaqa keh sakta hai)."
6201,"Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs (kisi ghulam ko) mera banda na kahey , to tum sab Allah ke bandey ho, albatta ye keh sakta hai: mera jawan, aur na ghulam ye kahey : mera rab (paalne wala) albatta mera saiyyed ( aaqa keh sakta hai)."
6202,abu-Muawiya aur Wakee donon ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki un donon ki hadis mein hai. ghulam apne aaqa ko mera maula na kahey . abu-Muawia ki hadis mein mazeed ye alfaz hain. kyonke tumhara Maula izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah hai.
6203,abu-Muawiya aur Wakee donon ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki un donon ki hadis mein hai. ghulam apne aaqa ko mera maula na kahey . abu-Muawia ki hadis mein mazeed ye alfaz hain. kyonke tumhara Maula izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah hai.
6204,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne kaha : ye hadisein hain jo hamein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, unhon-ne kuchh hadisein bayan kin, unmein (eik ye) hai. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs (apne ghulam ya kaneez se) ye na kahey : apne rab (paalanhaar) ko pilao , apne rab ko khilaao apne rab ko wuzu karao aur farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs ( kisi ko) mera rab na kahey, albatta mera aaqa aur mera Maula kahey. aur tum mein se koi yun na kahey : mera banda, meri bandi , albatta yun kahey , mera khaadim / jawan, meri khaadima , mera ladka ."
6205,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne kaha : ye hadisein hain jo hamein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, unhon-ne kuchh hadisein bayan kin, unmein (eik ye) hai. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs (apne ghulam ya kaneez se) ye na kahey : apne rab (paalanhaar) ko pilao , apne rab ko khilaao apne rab ko wuzu karao aur farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs ( kisi ko) mera rab na kahey, albatta mera aaqa aur mera Maula kahey. aur tum mein se koi yun na kahey : mera banda, meri bandi , albatta yun kahey , mera khaadim / jawan, meri khaadima , mera ladka ."
6206,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hadis bayan ki. abu-Kuraib Muhammad-bin-Alaa ne kaha : hamein abu-Usama ne hadis bayan ki. un donon ( Sufiyan aur abu-Usama ( ne Hisham se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs ye na kahey : mera ji (nafs, apna aap) gandaa ho gaya hai, balke ye kahey : meri tabeeat bojhal ho gaee hai. ye abu-Kuraib ki hadis ke alfaz hain. Abu-Bakar (ibne-Abi-Sheba) ne kaha : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat hai aur lekin ka lafz nahi kaha."
6207,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hadis bayan ki. abu-Kuraib Muhammad-bin-Alaa ne kaha : hamein abu-Usama ne hadis bayan ki. un donon ( Sufiyan aur abu-Usama ( ne Hisham se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs ye na kahey : mera ji (nafs, apna aap) gandaa ho gaya hai, balke ye kahey : meri tabeeat bojhal ho gaee hai. ye abu-Kuraib ki hadis ke alfaz hain. Abu-Bakar (ibne-Abi-Sheba) ne kaha : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat hai aur lekin ka lafz nahi kaha."
6208,abu-Kuraib ne kaha : hamein abu-Muawiya ne isi sanad ke sath ( yahi ( hadis bayan ki.
6209,abu-Kuraib ne kaha : hamein abu-Muawiya ne isi sanad ke sath ( yahi ( hadis bayan ki.
6210,"abu Amama-bin-Sahal-bin-Haneef ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya  tum mein se koi shakhs ye na kahey . mera ji gandaa ho gaya hai, balke ye kahey , ke mera ji bojhal ho gaya hai. (ya meri tabeeat kharaab ho gaee hai.)"
6211,"abu Amama-bin-Sahal-bin-Haneef ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya  tum mein se koi shakhs ye na kahey . mera ji gandaa ho gaya hai, balke ye kahey , ke mera ji bojhal ho gaya hai. (ya meri tabeeat kharaab ho gaee hai.)"
6212,"abu-Usama ne Shoba se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey khulaid-bin-Jafar ne abu-Nazara se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : Bani-Israeel mein aik pasta qaamat aurat do lambey qad ki aurton ke sath chala karti thi. us ne lakdi ki do taangein (aisey jootey ya mozey jinke talwon wala hissey bahut uncha tha) banwaaein aur soney ki aik band, dhakney wali anguthi banwaai. phir usey kastoori se bhar diya aur wo khushbuon mein sabse achi khushbu hai. phir wo un donon (lambi aurton) ke darmyan mein ho kar chali to log usey na pehchan sakey. is par us ne apne hath se is tarah ishara kiya aur Shoba ne (shagirdon ko dikhaaney ke liye) apna hath jhatkaa."
6213,"abu-Usama ne Shoba se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey khulaid-bin-Jafar ne abu-Nazara se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : Bani-Israeel mein aik pasta qaamat aurat do lambey qad ki aurton ke sath chala karti thi. us ne lakdi ki do taangein (aisey jootey ya mozey jinke talwon wala hissey bahut uncha tha) banwaaein aur soney ki aik band, dhakney wali anguthi banwaai. phir usey kastoori se bhar diya aur wo khushbuon mein sabse achi khushbu hai. phir wo un donon (lambi aurton) ke darmyan mein ho kar chali to log usey na pehchan sakey. is par us ne apne hath se is tarah ishara kiya aur Shoba ne (shagirdon ko dikhaaney ke liye) apna hath jhatkaa."
6214,"Yazid-bin-Harun ne Shoba se, unhon-ne khaleed-bin-Jafar aur mustamir se riwayat ki, un donon ne kaha : ham ne abu-Nazara ko suna, wo Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kar rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Bani-Israeel ki aik aurat ka zikr kiya, us ne apni anguthi mein kastoori bhar li thi aur kastoori sabse achi khushbu hai."
6215,"Yazid-bin-Harun ne Shoba se, unhon-ne khaleed-bin-Jafar aur mustamir se riwayat ki, un donon ne kaha : ham ne abu-Nazara ko suna, wo Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kar rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Bani-Israeel ki aik aurat ka zikr kiya, us ne apni anguthi mein kastoori bhar li thi aur kastoori sabse achi khushbu hai."
6216,Abdur-Rehman Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ko reaihaan ( khushbu daar phool ya tahni ( di jaey to wo usey mustarad na karey kyonke wo uthaney mein halki aur khushbu mein umda hai.
6217,Abdur-Rehman Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ko reaihaan ( khushbu daar phool ya tahni ( di jaey to wo usey mustarad na karey kyonke wo uthaney mein halki aur khushbu mein umda hai.
6218,"Naafe ne kaha : Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) jab khushbu ka dhuaan letey to aud ka dhuaan letey , usmein kisi aur cheez ki aamezish (milawat) na hoti aur kaafoor ka dhuaan letey , usmein kuchh aud mila letey , phir bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) isi tarah khushbu ka dhuaan letey (aur kapdon mein basaatey) they."
6219,"Naafe ne kaha : Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) jab khushbu ka dhuaan letey to aud ka dhuaan letey , usmein kisi aur cheez ki aamezish (milawat) na hoti aur kaafoor ka dhuaan letey , usmein kuchh aud mila letey , phir bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) isi tarah khushbu ka dhuaan letey (aur kapdon mein basaatey) they."
6220,"Amr Naqid aur ibne-abi-Umar , donon ne ibne-Uena se riwayat ki. ibne-abi-Umar ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hadis bayan ki. Ibrahim-bin-Maisra se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Amr-bin-shareed se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki kaha : aik din main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath sawar hua to aap ne farmaya : kya tumhen Umayya-bin-abi-salat ke she'ron mein se kuchh yad hai? maine arz kiya, ji haan. aap ne farmaya : to lao ( sunao ( maine aapko aik sher sunaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aur sunao. maine aik aur sher sunaya. aap ne farmaya : aur sunao. maine aik aur sher sunaya. aap ne farmaya : aur sunao. yahan tak ke maine aapko aik sau ash'aar sunaye."
