6222,"Zuhair-bin-Harab aur Ahmad-bin-Abda donon ne ibne-Uena se, unhon-ne Ibrahim-bin-Maisra se unhon-ne Amr-bin-shareed ya Yaqoob-bin-Aasim se, unhon-ne Hazrat shareed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. kaha mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sath sawar kiya, iske baad usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
6223,"Zuhair-bin-Harab aur Ahmad-bin-Abda donon ne ibne-Uena se, unhon-ne Ibrahim-bin-Maisra se unhon-ne Amr-bin-shareed ya Yaqoob-bin-Aasim se, unhon-ne Hazrat shareed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. kaha mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sath sawar kiya, iske baad usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
6224,"Moatamir-bin-Sulaiman aur Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi donon ne Abdullah-bin-Abdur-Rehman Taaifi se, unhon-ne Amr-bin-shareed se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey sher sunaney ke liye farmaya, Ibrahim-bin-Maisra ki riwayat ki tarah aur mazeed yun kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya qareeb tha ke wo musalman ho jata aur ibne-Mehdi ki hadis mein hai : wo apne ashaar mein musalman honey ke qareeb tha. (us ne taqriban wahi baatein kin jo aik musalman keh sakta hai.)"
6225,"Moatamir-bin-Sulaiman aur Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi donon ne Abdullah-bin-Abdur-Rehman Taaifi se, unhon-ne Amr-bin-shareed se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey sher sunaney ke liye farmaya, Ibrahim-bin-Maisra ki riwayat ki tarah aur mazeed yun kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya qareeb tha ke wo musalman ho jata aur ibne-Mehdi ki hadis mein hai : wo apne ashaar mein musalman honey ke qareeb tha. (us ne taqriban wahi baatein kin jo aik musalman keh sakta hai.)"
6226,"Sharik ne abdul-Malik-bin-Umair se unhon-ne abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : Arbon ne sher mein jo sabse umda baat kahi wo baat Labid ka ye jumla hai : sun rakho ! Allah ke siwa har cheez ( jiski ibadat ki jati hai) baatil hai. (doosra misra' hai : aur har nemat lazami taur par khatm honey wali hai.)"
6227,"Sharik ne abdul-Malik-bin-Umair se unhon-ne abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : Arbon ne sher mein jo sabse umda baat kahi wo baat Labid ka ye jumla hai : sun rakho ! Allah ke siwa har cheez ( jiski ibadat ki jati hai) baatil hai. (doosra misra' hai : aur har nemat lazami taur par khatm honey wali hai.)"
6228,"Sufiyan ne abdul-Malik-bin-Umair se riwayat ki, kaha : hamein abu-Salma ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : sabse sachchi baat jo kisi shaair ne kahi Labid ki baat hai. sun rakho ! Allah ke siwa har cheez ( jiski ibadat ki jati hai) baatil (ghalat) hai. aur qareeb tha ke Umayya-bin-abi-salat musalman ho jata."
