6244,"Amr Nafiz, Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim aur ibne-abi-Umar, sab ne ibne-Uena se riwayat ki, alfaz ibne-abi-Umar ke hain, kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Zohri se, unhon-ne abu-Salma se riwayat ki, kaha : main khuwab dekhta tha aur us se bukhar aur kapkapi jaisi kaifiyat mein mubtala ho jata tha, bas main chadar nahi odhta tha yahan tak ke main Hazrat Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se mila aur unhein ye baat batai to unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) suna, aap farma rahe they : ( sachcha ( khuwab Allah ki taraf se hai aur) bura ( khuwab shaitan ki taraf se, tum mein se koi shakhs jab aisa khuwab dekhey jo usey bura lagey to wo apni baain taraf teen baar thook de aur (jo us ne dekha ( iske shar se Allah ki panah talab karey to wo usey hargiz nuqsan nahi pahunchaeyga."
