6246,"ibne-abi-Umar ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne aale-Talha ke aazad karda ghulam Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehman, Saeed ke 2 beton Abde-Rabba aur Yahya aur Muhammad-bin Amr bin Alqama se hadis sunai, unhon-ne abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Hazrat Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki, un sab ne apni hadis mein abu-Salma ke us qaul ka zikr nahi kya : main khuwab dekhta tha jis se mujh par bukhar aur kapkapi taari ho jati thi magar main chadar nahi odhta tha."
6247,"ibne-abi-Umar ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne aale-Talha ke aazad karda ghulam Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehman, Saeed ke 2 beton Abde-Rabba aur Yahya aur Muhammad-bin Amr bin Alqama se hadis sunai, unhon-ne abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Hazrat Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki, un sab ne apni hadis mein abu-Salma ke us qaul ka zikr nahi kya : main khuwab dekhta tha jis se mujh par bukhar aur kapkapi taari ho jati thi magar main chadar nahi odhta tha."
6248,"Yunus aur Mamar donon ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath riwayat bayan ki, un donon ki hadis mein ye alfaz nahi hain : usse main bukhar aur kapkapi mein mubtala ho jata tha. Yunus ki hadis mein mazeed ye alfaz hain : wo jab neend se bedar ho to apni baain taraf teen baar thookey."
6249,"Yunus aur Mamar donon ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath riwayat bayan ki, un donon ki hadis mein ye alfaz nahi hain : usse main bukhar aur kapkapi mein mubtala ho jata tha. Yunus ki hadis mein mazeed ye alfaz hain : wo jab neend se bedar ho to apni baain taraf teen baar thookey."
6250,"abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne kaha : maine Hazrat abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, kehtey they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna, ( sachcha ( khuwab Allah ki taraf se hai aur) bura ( khuwab shetan ki taraf se hai, jab tum mein se koi shakhs aisa khuwab dekhey jo usey bura lagey to wo apni baain taraf teen baar thook de aur us (khuwab) ke shar se Allah ki panah maangey to wo khuwab usey hargiz nuqsan nahi pahuncha sakega. to (abu-Salma ne) kaha : kabhi-kabhi mein aisa khuwab dekhta jo mujh par pahaad se bhi zyada bhari hota tha, phir yahi hua ke maine ye hadis suni to ab main uski parwa nahi karta."
6251,"abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne kaha : maine Hazrat abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, kehtey they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna, ( sachcha ( khuwab Allah ki taraf se hai aur) bura ( khuwab shetan ki taraf se hai, jab tum mein se koi shakhs aisa khuwab dekhey jo usey bura lagey to wo apni baain taraf teen baar thook de aur us (khuwab) ke shar se Allah ki panah maangey to wo khuwab usey hargiz nuqsan nahi pahuncha sakega. to (abu-Salma ne) kaha : kabhi-kabhi mein aisa khuwab dekhta jo mujh par pahaad se bhi zyada bhari hota tha, phir yahi hua ke maine ye hadis suni to ab main uski parwa nahi karta."
6252,"Quteba aur Muhammad-bin Rumeh ne Lais-bin-Sad se riwayat ki, Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne kaha : hamein Abdul-Wahab Saqafi ne hadis bayan ki, abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein Abdullah-bin-Numair ne hadis bayan ki, un sab (Leis abdul-wahaab Saqafi aur Abdullah-bin-Numair ( ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se isi sanad ke sath riwayat bayan ki, Saqafi ki riwayat mein hai ke abu-Salma ne kaha : main khuwab dekha karta tha. Leis aur ibne-Numair ki riwayat mein hadis ke aakhir tak abu-Salma ka jo qaul ( manqul ( hai wo maujood nahi, ibne- Rumeh ne us hadis ki riwayat mein mazeed ye kaha hai : wo jis karwat par leta hua tha us se dusri karwat ho jaey."
6253,"Quteba aur Muhammad-bin Rumeh ne Lais-bin-Sad se riwayat ki, Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne kaha : hamein Abdul-Wahab Saqafi ne hadis bayan ki, abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein Abdullah-bin-Numair ne hadis bayan ki, un sab (Leis abdul-wahaab Saqafi aur Abdullah-bin-Numair ( ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se isi sanad ke sath riwayat bayan ki, Saqafi ki riwayat mein hai ke abu-Salma ne kaha : main khuwab dekha karta tha. Leis aur ibne-Numair ki riwayat mein hadis ke aakhir tak abu-Salma ka jo qaul ( manqul ( hai wo maujood nahi, ibne- Rumeh ne us hadis ki riwayat mein mazeed ye kaha hai : wo jis karwat par leta hua tha us se dusri karwat ho jaey."
6254,"Amr-bin-Haris ne Abde-Rabba bin Saeed se, unhon-ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, ke aap ne farmaya : achchha khuwab Allah Taala ki taraf se hai, aur bura khuwab shaitan ki taraf se hai, jis shakhs ne koi khuwab dekha aur is mein se koi cheez usko buri lagi to wo ( teen baar ( apni baain taraf thookey aur shaitan ke shar se Allah ki panah maangey to wo khuwab usko koi nuqsan nahi pahunchaeyga aur ye khuwab wo kisi ko bayan na kare. agar achchha khuwab dekhey to khush ho aur sirf usko bataaey jo us se mohabbat karta hai."
6255,"Amr-bin-Haris ne Abde-Rabba bin Saeed se, unhon-ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, ke aap ne farmaya : achchha khuwab Allah Taala ki taraf se hai, aur bura khuwab shaitan ki taraf se hai, jis shakhs ne koi khuwab dekha aur is mein se koi cheez usko buri lagi to wo ( teen baar ( apni baain taraf thookey aur shaitan ke shar se Allah ki panah maangey to wo khuwab usko koi nuqsan nahi pahunchaeyga aur ye khuwab wo kisi ko bayan na kare. agar achchha khuwab dekhey to khush ho aur sirf usko bataaey jo us se mohabbat karta hai."
6256,"Shoba ne Abde-Rabba bin Saeed se, unhon-ne abu-Salma se riwayat ki, kaha : kabhi-kabhi mein aisa khuwab dekhta tha jis se main bimar pad jata tha, yahan tak ke meri Hazrat abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat hui to unhon-ne kaha : main bhi kabhi-kabhi khuwab dekhta tha jo mujhey bimar kar detey they, yahan tak ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna, achchha khuwab Allah ki taraf se hota hai, jab tum mein se koi shakhs achchha khuwab dekhey to wo sirf us shakhs ko bataaey jo (is se) mohabbat karta ho aur agar na-pasandida khuwab dekhey to teen baar apni baain taraf thookey aur teen baar shaitan aur us khuwab ke shar se Allah ki panah maangey aur wo khuwab kisi ko na bataaey to wo usey koi nuqsan nahi pahunchaeyga."
6257,"Shoba ne Abde-Rabba bin Saeed se, unhon-ne abu-Salma se riwayat ki, kaha : kabhi-kabhi mein aisa khuwab dekhta tha jis se main bimar pad jata tha, yahan tak ke meri Hazrat abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat hui to unhon-ne kaha : main bhi kabhi-kabhi khuwab dekhta tha jo mujhey bimar kar detey they, yahan tak ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna, achchha khuwab Allah ki taraf se hota hai, jab tum mein se koi shakhs achchha khuwab dekhey to wo sirf us shakhs ko bataaey jo (is se) mohabbat karta ho aur agar na-pasandida khuwab dekhey to teen baar apni baain taraf thookey aur teen baar shaitan aur us khuwab ke shar se Allah ki panah maangey aur wo khuwab kisi ko na bataaey to wo usey koi nuqsan nahi pahunchaeyga."
6258,Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs aisa khuwab dekhey jo usey bura lagey to teen baar apni baain taraf thookey aur teen baar shaitan se Allah ki panah maangey aur jis karwat leta hua tha usey badal ley.
