6260,"abdul-Wahab Saqafi ne Ayub sakhtiyan se, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin Sirin se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : (qiyamat ka ( zamana qareeb aa jaeyga to kisi musalman ka khuwab jhoota na niklega . tum mein se unke khuwab zyada sachey hongey jo baat mein zyada sachey hongey. padhi. musalman ka khuwab nabwooat ke pentaalis hisson mein se aik (pentaaleeswan) hissa hai khuwab teen tarah ke hotey hain. achchha khuwab Allah ki taraf se khush khabri hoti hai. aik khuwab shaitan ki taraf se ghamgeen karne ke liye hota hai. aur aik khuwab wo jis mein insan khud apne aap se baat karta hai. (iske apne khayaal ki karfarmai hoti hai.) agar tum mein se koi shakhs na-pasandida khuwab dekhey to khada ho jaey aur Namaz padhey aur logon ko uske barey mein kuchh na bataaey. farmaya : (paon ki) bedi (khuwab mein dekhna) mujhey pasand hai aur (galey ka ( tauq na-pasand hai. bedi Deen mein Sabit qadmi (ki alamat ( hai. ( Saqafi ne Ayub sakhtiyan se naql kartey huey kaha : ( to mujhey malum nahi ke ye baat hadis (nabawi) mein hai ya Ibne-Sirin ne kahi hai."
