6290,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna, jis shakhs ne khuwab mein mujhey dekha wo an-qareeb bedaari mein bhi mujhey dekh lega ya (farmaya :) mano usne mujh ko bedaari ke aalim mein dekha, shaitan meri sura ikhtiyar nahi kar sakta."
