6296,"Leis ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne mujhey khuwab mein dekha us ne mujhii ko dekha, kyonke shaitan meri sura ikhtiyar nahi kar sakta aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (ye bhi) farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs bura khuwab dekhey to wo neend ke aalim main apne sath shaitan ke khelney ki kisi doosrey ko khabar na de."
6297,"Leis ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne mujhey khuwab mein dekha us ne mujhii ko dekha, kyonke shaitan meri sura ikhtiyar nahi kar sakta aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (ye bhi) farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs bura khuwab dekhey to wo neend ke aalim main apne sath shaitan ke khelney ki kisi doosrey ko khabar na de."
6298,"Zakariya-bin Ishaq ne kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne neend mein mujhey dekha to usne mujhi ko dekha kyonke shaitan ke bas mein nahi ke wo meri mushabihat (similarity) ikhtiyar kar sakey."
6299,"Zakariya-bin Ishaq ne kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne neend mein mujhey dekha to usne mujhi ko dekha kyonke shaitan ke bas mein nahi ke wo meri mushabihat (similarity) ikhtiyar kar sakey."
6300,"abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke dehati (badwi) ne, jo aap ke paas aaya tha, aap se kaha : maine khuwab mein dekha hai ke mera sar kat gaya hai aur main uske peechhey bhag raha hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey daanta aur Farmaya : neend ke aalim mein apne sath shaitan ke khelney ke barey mein kisi ko mat bataao."
6301,"abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke dehati (badwi) ne, jo aap ke paas aaya tha, aap se kaha : maine khuwab mein dekha hai ke mera sar kat gaya hai aur main uske peechhey bhag raha hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey daanta aur Farmaya : neend ke aalim mein apne sath shaitan ke khelney ke barey mein kisi ko mat bataao."
6302,"Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik dehati Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : Allah ke rasool! maine khuwab mein dekha ke mere sar ko talwaar ka nishan banaya gaya, wo ludhakta hua ja raha hai aur main uske peechhey daud raha hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dehati se farmaya : neend ki haalat main shaitan tumharey sath jo chhed khaani karey wo logon ko na bataao. (hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : maine iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khutba detey huey suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : khuwab mein shaitan tumharey sath jo chhed khuwaani karey tum mein se koi iske barey mein logon ke sath baatein na kare."
6303,"Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik dehati Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : Allah ke rasool! maine khuwab mein dekha ke mere sar ko talwaar ka nishan banaya gaya, wo ludhakta hua ja raha hai aur main uske peechhey daud raha hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dehati se farmaya : neend ki haalat main shaitan tumharey sath jo chhed khaani karey wo logon ko na bataao. (hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : maine iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khutba detey huey suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : khuwab mein shaitan tumharey sath jo chhed khuwaani karey tum mein se koi iske barey mein logon ke sath baatein na kare."
6304,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur abu-Saeed ashajj ne kaha : hamein Wakee ne Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maine khuwab mein dekha ke mera sar kaat diya gaya. Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hans padey aur farmaya : jab khuwab mein shaitan tum mein se kisi ke sath chhed khani karey to wo logon ko na bataata phirey Abu-Bakar ki riwayat mein hai : jab tum mein se kisi ke sath chhed khani ki jaey. aur unhon-ne shaitan ka zikr nahi kya."
6305,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur abu-Saeed ashajj ne kaha : hamein Wakee ne Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maine khuwab mein dekha ke mera sar kaat diya gaya. Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hans padey aur farmaya : jab khuwab mein shaitan tum mein se kisi ke sath chhed khani karey to wo logon ko na bataata phirey Abu-Bakar ki riwayat mein hai : jab tum mein se kisi ke sath chhed khani ki jaey. aur unhon-ne shaitan ka zikr nahi kya."
6306,"Muhammad-bin Harab ne Yunus Zubaidi se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Zohri ne Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah se khabar di ke Ibne-Abbas ya Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) hadis sunaya kartey they ke aik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur ibne- Wahab ne hamein khabar di, kaha : mujhey Yunus ( Zubeda ( ne ibne-Shahab se khabar di ke Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullaah-bin-Utba ne unhein baghair shak ke bataya ke Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) hadis bayan kya kartey they ke aik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kehney laga ke ya Rasulullah ! maine raat ko khuwab mein dekha ke badal ke tukdey se ghi aur shehad tapak raha hai, log usko apne lappon se letey hain koi zyada leta hai aur koi kam aur maine dekha ke aasman se zamin tak aik rassii latkii hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usko pakad kar uper chadh gaey. phir aap ke baad aik shakhs ne usko thaamaa , wo bhi chadh gaya. phir aik aur shakhs ne thaamaa wo bhi chadh gaya. phir aik aur shakhs ne thaamaa to wo toot gaee, phir jad gaee aur wo bhi uper chala gaya. ye sun kar saiyedna Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah! mera bap aap par qurbaan ho mujhey uski tabeer bayan karne dijiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchha bayan kar. saiyedna Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke wo badal ka tukda to Islam hai aur ghi aur shehad se Quran ki halaawat aur narmi murad hai aur log jo zyada aur kam letey hain wo bhi kuch ko bahut Quran yad hai aur kuch ko kam aur wo rassi jo aasman se zamin tak latki hai wo deene-haq hai jis par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hain. phir Allah Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko usi Deen par apne paas bula lega aap ke baad aik aur shakhs (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka khaleefa) usko thaamega wo bhi isi tarah chadh jaeyga phir aur aik shakhs thaamega aur uska bhi yahi haal hoga. phir aik aur shakhs thaamega to kuchh khalal padega lekin wo khalal aakhir mit jaeyga aur wo bhi chadh jaeyga ya Rasulullah ! mere maan-baap aap par qurbaan hon mujh se bayan farmaiye ke maine theek tabeer bayan ki? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tu ney kuchh theek kaha kuchh ghalat kaha, saiyedna Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Allah ki qism ya Rasulullah ! aap bayan kijiye ke maine kya ghalati ki? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qism mat kha ."
6307,"Muhammad-bin Harab ne Yunus Zubaidi se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Zohri ne Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah se khabar di ke Ibne-Abbas ya Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) hadis sunaya kartey they ke aik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur ibne- Wahab ne hamein khabar di, kaha : mujhey Yunus ( Zubeda ( ne ibne-Shahab se khabar di ke Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullaah-bin-Utba ne unhein baghair shak ke bataya ke Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) hadis bayan kya kartey they ke aik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kehney laga ke ya Rasulullah ! maine raat ko khuwab mein dekha ke badal ke tukdey se ghi aur shehad tapak raha hai, log usko apne lappon se letey hain koi zyada leta hai aur koi kam aur maine dekha ke aasman se zamin tak aik rassii latkii hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usko pakad kar uper chadh gaey. phir aap ke baad aik shakhs ne usko thaamaa , wo bhi chadh gaya. phir aik aur shakhs ne thaamaa wo bhi chadh gaya. phir aik aur shakhs ne thaamaa to wo toot gaee, phir jad gaee aur wo bhi uper chala gaya. ye sun kar saiyedna Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah! mera bap aap par qurbaan ho mujhey uski tabeer bayan karne dijiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchha bayan kar. saiyedna Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke wo badal ka tukda to Islam hai aur ghi aur shehad se Quran ki halaawat aur narmi murad hai aur log jo zyada aur kam letey hain wo bhi kuch ko bahut Quran yad hai aur kuch ko kam aur wo rassi jo aasman se zamin tak latki hai wo deene-haq hai jis par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hain. phir Allah Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko usi Deen par apne paas bula lega aap ke baad aik aur shakhs (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka khaleefa) usko thaamega wo bhi isi tarah chadh jaeyga phir aur aik shakhs thaamega aur uska bhi yahi haal hoga. phir aik aur shakhs thaamega to kuchh khalal padega lekin wo khalal aakhir mit jaeyga aur wo bhi chadh jaeyga ya Rasulullah ! mere maan-baap aap par qurbaan hon mujh se bayan farmaiye ke maine theek tabeer bayan ki? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tu ney kuchh theek kaha kuchh ghalat kaha, saiyedna Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Allah ki qism ya Rasulullah ! aap bayan kijiye ke maine kya ghalati ki? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qism mat kha ."
6308,"Sufiyan ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Uhud se waapsi par aik aadmi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha : Allah ke rasool! maine aaj raat khuwab mein badal ke aik tukdey ko saaya figan dekha hai jo shehad aur ghi tapka raha tha, Yunus ki hadis ke mafhoom ke mutabiq ( hadis bayan ki.)"
6309,"Sufiyan ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Uhud se waapsi par aik aadmi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha : Allah ke rasool! maine aaj raat khuwab mein badal ke aik tukdey ko saaya figan dekha hai jo shehad aur ghi tapka raha tha, Yunus ki hadis ke mafhoom ke mutabiq ( hadis bayan ki.)"
6310,"Abdur-Razzaq ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Mamar ne Zohri se khabar di unhon-ne Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullah-bin-Utba se (aagey) Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ya Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, Abdur-Razzaq ne kaha ke Mamar kabhi kehtey they : Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai aur kabhi kehtey they Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke aik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kaha : maine aaj raat aik badal ko saaya-figan dekha hai. un sab ki bayan ki hui hadis ke mafhoom ke mutabiq."
6311,"Abdur-Razzaq ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Mamar ne Zohri se khabar di unhon-ne Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullah-bin-Utba se (aagey) Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ya Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, Abdur-Razzaq ne kaha ke Mamar kabhi kehtey they : Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai aur kabhi kehtey they Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke aik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kaha : maine aaj raat aik badal ko saaya-figan dekha hai. un sab ki bayan ki hui hadis ke mafhoom ke mutabiq."
6312,"Salman bin Kasir ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) se ye farmaya kartey they : tum mein se jis shakhs ne khuwab dekha hai, wo bayan karey, main uski tabeer bataunga. kaha : to aik shakhs aaya aur kehney laga : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)! maine aik badal ko saaya-figan dekha. jis tarah un sab (bayan karne walon) ki hadis hai."
6313,"Salman bin Kasir ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) se ye farmaya kartey they : tum mein se jis shakhs ne khuwab dekha hai, wo bayan karey, main uski tabeer bataunga. kaha : to aik shakhs aaya aur kehney laga : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)! maine aik badal ko saaya-figan dekha. jis tarah un sab (bayan karne walon) ki hadis hai."
6314,"saiyedna Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine aik raat ko neend ki haalat mein dekhney waley ki tarah (khuwab) dekha ke jaisey ham Aqba bin Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar mein hain, to hamarey aagey tar khajoorein laai gain, jisko ibne-taab ki khajoor ka naam diya jata hai. maine uski tabeer ye ki ke hamara darja duniya mein buland hoga, aakhirat mein nek anjam hoga aur yaqinan hamara Deen behtar aur umda hai."
6315,"saiyedna Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine aik raat ko neend ki haalat mein dekhney waley ki tarah (khuwab) dekha ke jaisey ham Aqba bin Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar mein hain, to hamarey aagey tar khajoorein laai gain, jisko ibne-taab ki khajoor ka naam diya jata hai. maine uski tabeer ye ki ke hamara darja duniya mein buland hoga, aakhirat mein nek anjam hoga aur yaqinan hamara Deen behtar aur umda hai."
6316,"sakhr bin Juweriya ne hamein Naafe se hadis sunai ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine khuwab mein khud ko dekha ke main aik miswak se daant saaf kar raha hun, us waqt 2 aadmiyon ne ( miswak hasil karne ke liye) meri tawajjoh apni taraf karaai. unmein aik doosrey se bada tha, maine wo miswak chhotey ko de di, phir mujh se kaha gaya : badey ko dein to maine wo badey ko di."
6317,"sakhr bin Juweriya ne hamein Naafe se hadis sunai ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine khuwab mein khud ko dekha ke main aik miswak se daant saaf kar raha hun, us waqt 2 aadmiyon ne ( miswak hasil karne ke liye) meri tawajjoh apni taraf karaai. unmein aik doosrey se bada tha, maine wo miswak chhotey ko de di, phir mujh se kaha gaya : badey ko dein to maine wo badey ko di."
6318,"saiyedna abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine khuwab mein dekha ke main Makka se us zamin ki taraf hijrat karta hun jahan khajoor ke darakht hain, mera guman yamama aur hijr ki taraf gaya lekin wo Madina nikla, jiska naam yasrib bhi hai aur maine apne usi khuwab mein dekha ke maine talwaar ko hilaaya to wo uper se toot gaee, uski tabeer Uhud ke din musalmanon ki shikast nikli. phir maine talwaar ko dusri baar hilaya to aagey se waisi hi Sabit aur achi ho gaee. uski tabeer ye nikli ke Allah Taala ne fateh naseeb ki aur musalmanon ki jamat qaaim ho gaee (yani jange-Uhud ke baad khaibar aur Makka fateh hua aur Islam ke lashkar ne zor pakda (aur maine usi khuwab mein gaaein dekhein (jo kaati jati thin) aur Allah Taala behtar hai) jaisey ye jumla bola jata hai Allah khair (us se musalmanon ke wo log murad they jo Uhud mein Shahid huey aur khair se murad wo khair thi jo Allah Taala ne iske baad bheji aur sachchai ka sawab jo Allah Taala ne hamein badr ke baad inayat kya."
6319,"saiyedna abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine khuwab mein dekha ke main Makka se us zamin ki taraf hijrat karta hun jahan khajoor ke darakht hain, mera guman yamama aur hijr ki taraf gaya lekin wo Madina nikla, jiska naam yasrib bhi hai aur maine apne usi khuwab mein dekha ke maine talwaar ko hilaaya to wo uper se toot gaee, uski tabeer Uhud ke din musalmanon ki shikast nikli. phir maine talwaar ko dusri baar hilaya to aagey se waisi hi Sabit aur achi ho gaee. uski tabeer ye nikli ke Allah Taala ne fateh naseeb ki aur musalmanon ki jamat qaaim ho gaee (yani jange-Uhud ke baad khaibar aur Makka fateh hua aur Islam ke lashkar ne zor pakda (aur maine usi khuwab mein gaaein dekhein (jo kaati jati thin) aur Allah Taala behtar hai) jaisey ye jumla bola jata hai Allah khair (us se musalmanon ke wo log murad they jo Uhud mein Shahid huey aur khair se murad wo khair thi jo Allah Taala ne iske baad bheji aur sachchai ka sawab jo Allah Taala ne hamein badr ke baad inayat kya."
6320,"saiyedna Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Musailma kazzaab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein Madina Munawra mein aaya aur kehney laga ke agar Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey apne baad khilafat dein to main unki pairwi karta hun. Musailma kazzaab apne sath apni qaum ke bahut se log lekar aaya tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uske paas tashrif laey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Sabit bin Qais-bin Shamas (Raziallahu anhu) they aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath mein lakdi ka aik tukda tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Musailma ke logon ke paas thahrey aur farmaya ke aey Musailma! agar to mujh se ye lakdi ka tukda maangey to bhi tujh ko na doonga aur main Allah ke hukm ke khilaf terey barey mein faisla karne wala nahi aur agar to mera kehna na maanega to Allah Taala tujh ko qatl karega (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye farmana sahi ho gaya) aur yaqinan tujhey wahi janta hun jo mujhey terey barey mein khuwab mein dikhaya gaya hai aur ye Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) tujhey meri taraf se jawab dega. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan se chaley gaey. saiyedna Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine logon se puchha ke ye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya farmaya ke to wahi hai jo mujhey khuwab mein terey barey mein dikhlaaya gaya, to saiyedna Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bayan kya ke main so raha tha ke maine ( khuwab mein) apne hath mein soney ke 2 kangan dekhey, wo mujhey burey malum huey aur khuwab hi mein mujh par ilqa kya gaya ke unko phoonk maaro, maine phoonka to wo donon ud gaey. maine unki tabeer ye ki ke us se murad 2 jhootey hain, jo mere baad niklengey . unmein se aik Ansa sanaa wala aur doosra yamaama wala ( Musailma kazzaab ( hai."
6321,"saiyedna Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Musailma kazzaab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein Madina Munawra mein aaya aur kehney laga ke agar Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey apne baad khilafat dein to main unki pairwi karta hun. Musailma kazzaab apne sath apni qaum ke bahut se log lekar aaya tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uske paas tashrif laey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Sabit bin Qais-bin Shamas (Raziallahu anhu) they aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath mein lakdi ka aik tukda tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Musailma ke logon ke paas thahrey aur farmaya ke aey Musailma! agar to mujh se ye lakdi ka tukda maangey to bhi tujh ko na doonga aur main Allah ke hukm ke khilaf terey barey mein faisla karne wala nahi aur agar to mera kehna na maanega to Allah Taala tujh ko qatl karega (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye farmana sahi ho gaya) aur yaqinan tujhey wahi janta hun jo mujhey terey barey mein khuwab mein dikhaya gaya hai aur ye Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) tujhey meri taraf se jawab dega. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan se chaley gaey. saiyedna Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine logon se puchha ke ye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya farmaya ke to wahi hai jo mujhey khuwab mein terey barey mein dikhlaaya gaya, to saiyedna Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bayan kya ke main so raha tha ke maine ( khuwab mein) apne hath mein soney ke 2 kangan dekhey, wo mujhey burey malum huey aur khuwab hi mein mujh par ilqa kya gaya ke unko phoonk maaro, maine phoonka to wo donon ud gaey. maine unki tabeer ye ki ke us se murad 2 jhootey hain, jo mere baad niklengey . unmein se aik Ansa sanaa wala aur doosra yamaama wala ( Musailma kazzaab ( hai."
6322,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : ye hadisein hain jo hamein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin. unhon-ne kai hadisein bayan kin, unmein se (eik ( ye hai : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab main so raha tha to zamin ke khazaaney mere paas laey gaey. us ( khazaaney ko laney waale) ne soney ke 2 kangan mere hathon mein daal diye, ye donon mujh par nagawar guzrey aur unhon-ne mujhey tashwish mein mubtala kar diya, to meri taraf wahi ki gaee ke un donon ko phoonk maarein , maine donon ko phoonk maari to wo chaley gaey. maine unse murad 2 kazzaab liye, mein unke beech main ( muqeem ( hun. aik (daain hath par waaqe) sanaa ka rehney wala aur doosra baain hath par) yamaama ka rehney wala."
6323,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : ye hadisein hain jo hamein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin. unhon-ne kai hadisein bayan kin, unmein se (eik ( ye hai : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab main so raha tha to zamin ke khazaaney mere paas laey gaey. us ( khazaaney ko laney waale) ne soney ke 2 kangan mere hathon mein daal diye, ye donon mujh par nagawar guzrey aur unhon-ne mujhey tashwish mein mubtala kar diya, to meri taraf wahi ki gaee ke un donon ko phoonk maarein , maine donon ko phoonk maari to wo chaley gaey. maine unse murad 2 kazzaab liye, mein unke beech main ( muqeem ( hun. aik (daain hath par waaqe) sanaa ka rehney wala aur doosra baain hath par) yamaama ka rehney wala."
6324,"Hazrat Samra-bin-Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) subah ki Namaz padhney ke baad logon ki taraf rukh kartey aur farmatey : tum mein se kisi ne guzishta raat koi khuwab dekha?"
6325,"Hazrat Samra-bin-Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) subah ki Namaz padhney ke baad logon ki taraf rukh kartey aur farmatey : tum mein se kisi ne guzishta raat koi khuwab dekha?"
6326,"abu Ammar Shaddad se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Hazrat Wasila bin Isqaa (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : Allah Taala ne Hazrat Ismail (Alaihissalam) ki aulad mein se kinaana ko muntakhab kya aur kinaana mein se Quraish ko muntakhab kya aur Quraish mein se banu-Haashim ko muntakhab kya aur banu-Haashim mein se mujh ko muntakhab kya."
6327,"abu Ammar Shaddad se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Hazrat Wasila bin Isqaa (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : Allah Taala ne Hazrat Ismail (Alaihissalam) ki aulad mein se kinaana ko muntakhab kya aur kinaana mein se Quraish ko muntakhab kya aur Quraish mein se banu-Haashim ko muntakhab kya aur banu-Haashim mein se mujh ko muntakhab kya."
6328,"Hazrat Jaabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main Makka mein us patthar ko achi tarah pehchanta hun jo besat (nabi banaey janey) se pahley mujhey salam kya karta tha, bila shubah main us patthar ko ab bhi pehchanta hun."
6329,"Hazrat Jaabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main Makka mein us patthar ko achi tarah pehchanta hun jo besat (nabi banaey janey) se pahley mujhey salam kya karta tha, bila shubah main us patthar ko ab bhi pehchanta hun."
6330,"Abdullah-bin Farukh ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main qiyamat ke din (tamam) aulad Adam ka sardaar hunga, pahlaa shakhs hunga jiski qabr khulegi, sabse pahlaa shafaat karne wala hunga aur sabse pahla hunga jiski shafaat qabool hogi."
6331,"Abdullah-bin Farukh ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main qiyamat ke din (tamam) aulad Adam ka sardaar hunga, pahlaa shakhs hunga jiski qabr khulegi, sabse pahlaa shafaat karne wala hunga aur sabse pahla hunga jiski shafaat qabool hogi."
6332,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pani talab farmaya to aik khula hua piyala laya gaya, log us se wuzu karne lagey, maine sath se usi tak ki tadaad ka andaza lagaya, main (apni aankhon se) us pani ki taraf dekhney laga, wo aap ki ungliyon ke darmyan se phoot raha tha."
6333,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pani talab farmaya to aik khula hua piyala laya gaya, log us se wuzu karne lagey, maine sath se usi tak ki tadaad ka andaza lagaya, main (apni aankhon se) us pani ki taraf dekhney laga, wo aap ki ungliyon ke darmyan se phoot raha tha."
6334,"Ishaq bin-Abdullah-bin abi Talha ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke Asr ka waqt aa chuka tha, logon ne wuzu ka pani talash kya aur unhein na mila, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas wuzu ka kuchh pani laya gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us bartan mein apna hath rakh diya aur logon ko us pani mein se wuzu ka hukm diya. kaha : to maine dekha ke pani aap ki ungliyon ke nichey se phoot raha tha aur logon ne apne aakhiri aadmi tak (is se) wuzu kar liya."
6335,"Ishaq bin-Abdullah-bin abi Talha ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke Asr ka waqt aa chuka tha, logon ne wuzu ka pani talash kya aur unhein na mila, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas wuzu ka kuchh pani laya gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us bartan mein apna hath rakh diya aur logon ko us pani mein se wuzu ka hukm diya. kaha : to maine dekha ke pani aap ki ungliyon ke nichey se phoot raha tha aur logon ne apne aakhiri aadmi tak (is se) wuzu kar liya."
6336,"Muaz ke walid Hisham ne Qatada se riwayat ki, kaha : hamein Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab ( maqam ( Zaura mein they { aur Zauraa Madina mein masjid aur bazar ke nazdeek aik maqam hai} Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pani ka aik piyala mangwaya aur apni hatheli usmein rakh di, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ungliyon ke darmyan se pani phootney laga aur tamam ashaab (Raziallahu anhu) ne wuzu kar liya. Qatada ne kaha ke maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke aey abu-Hamza! us waqt aap kitney aadmi hongey? saiyedna Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke teen so ke qareeb they."
6337,"Muaz ke walid Hisham ne Qatada se riwayat ki, kaha : hamein Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab ( maqam ( Zaura mein they { aur Zauraa Madina mein masjid aur bazar ke nazdeek aik maqam hai} Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pani ka aik piyala mangwaya aur apni hatheli usmein rakh di, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ungliyon ke darmyan se pani phootney laga aur tamam ashaab (Raziallahu anhu) ne wuzu kar liya. Qatada ne kaha ke maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke aey abu-Hamza! us waqt aap kitney aadmi hongey? saiyedna Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke teen so ke qareeb they."
6338,"Saeed ne Qatada se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zaura mein they, aap ke paas pani ka aik bartan laya gaya, wo aap ki ungliyon ke uper tak bhi nahi aata tha (jis mein aap ki ungliyan bhi nahi doobti thin) ya is qadr tha ke (shayad (aap ki ungliyon ko dhanp leta. phir Hisham ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya."
6339,"Saeed ne Qatada se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zaura mein they, aap ke paas pani ka aik bartan laya gaya, wo aap ki ungliyon ke uper tak bhi nahi aata tha (jis mein aap ki ungliyan bhi nahi doobti thin) ya is qadr tha ke (shayad (aap ki ungliyon ko dhanp leta. phir Hisham ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya."
6340,"Saiyedna Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke umme-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik kuppi mein bataur tohfa ghi bheja karti thin, phir uske betey aatey aur us se saalan maangtey aur ghar mein kuchh na hota to umme-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) us kuppi ke paas jaati, to usmein ghi hota. isi tarah hamesha uske ghar ka saalan qaaim rehta . aik baar umme-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne (hirs karke) us kuppi ko nichod liya, phir wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaein to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne istifsaar farmaya ke kya tum ne usko nichod liya hai? unhon-ne jawab diya haan to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar to usko yun hi rehney deti (aur zarurat ke waqt leti) to wo hamesha qaaim rehta."
6341,"Saiyedna Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke umme-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik kuppi mein bataur tohfa ghi bheja karti thin, phir uske betey aatey aur us se saalan maangtey aur ghar mein kuchh na hota to umme-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) us kuppi ke paas jaati, to usmein ghi hota. isi tarah hamesha uske ghar ka saalan qaaim rehta . aik baar umme-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne (hirs karke) us kuppi ko nichod liya, phir wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaein to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne istifsaar farmaya ke kya tum ne usko nichod liya hai? unhon-ne jawab diya haan to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar to usko yun hi rehney deti (aur zarurat ke waqt leti) to wo hamesha qaaim rehta."
6342,"Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein khana hasil karne ke liye aaya, aap ne usey aadha wasq (taqriban 120Kg) jo diye to wo aadmi, uski biwi aur un donon ke mehman musalsal usmein se khaatey rahe, yahan tak ke (eik din) us ne unko maap liya, phir wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya (aur maajraa bataya ( to aap ne farmaya : agar tum usko na maaptey to musalsal usmein se khaatey rahtey aur ye ( silsile ( tumharey liye qaaim rehta ."
6343,"Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein khana hasil karne ke liye aaya, aap ne usey aadha wasq (taqriban 120Kg) jo diye to wo aadmi, uski biwi aur un donon ke mehman musalsal usmein se khaatey rahe, yahan tak ke (eik din) us ne unko maap liya, phir wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya (aur maajraa bataya ( to aap ne farmaya : agar tum usko na maaptey to musalsal usmein se khaatey rahtey aur ye ( silsile ( tumharey liye qaaim rehta ."
6344,"hamein abu Ali Hanfi ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Malik-bin-Anas ne abu-Zubair Makki se hadis bayan ki ke abu Tufail Aamir bin Wasila (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein khabar di, unhein Hazrat Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya, kaha : ke ham jange-Tabook ke mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath us saal nikley. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us safar mein 2 namazon ko jama kartey they. to Zohar aur Asr donon mila kar padhein aur maghrib aur isha mila kar padhin. aik din Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz mein der ki. phir nikley aur Zohar aur Asr mila kar padhein phir andar chaley gaey. phir iske baad nikley to maghrib aur isha mila kar padhein iske baad farmaya ke kal tum log agar Allah Taala ne chaha to Tabook ke chashmey par pahunchogey aur din nikalney se pahley nahi pahunch sakogey aur jo koi tum mein se us chashmey ke paas jaey, to uske pani ko hath na lagaey jab tak main na aaun. saiyedna Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke phir ham us chashmey par pahunchey aur ham se pahley wahan 2 aadmi pahunch gaey they. chashme ke pani ka ye haal tha ke jooti ke tasme ke barabar hoga, wo bhi ahista-ahista beh raha tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un donon aadmiyon se puchha ke tum ne iske pani mein hath lagaya? unhon-ne kaha ke haan, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko bura kaha (is liye ke unhon-ne hukm ke khilaf kya tha) aur Allah Taala ko jo manzoor tha wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko sunaya. phir logon ne chulluon se thoda thoda pani aik bartan mein jama kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne donon hath aur munh usmein dhoya, phir wo pani us chashme mein daal diya to wo chashma josh mar kar behney laga aur logon ne (apne janwaron aur aadmiyon ko) pani pilaana shuru kya. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey Muaz! agar teri zindagi rahi to to dekhega ke yahan jo jagah hai wo ghaney baghaat se lahlaha uthegi."
6345,"hamein abu Ali Hanfi ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Malik-bin-Anas ne abu-Zubair Makki se hadis bayan ki ke abu Tufail Aamir bin Wasila (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein khabar di, unhein Hazrat Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya, kaha : ke ham jange-Tabook ke mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath us saal nikley. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us safar mein 2 namazon ko jama kartey they. to Zohar aur Asr donon mila kar padhein aur maghrib aur isha mila kar padhin. aik din Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz mein der ki. phir nikley aur Zohar aur Asr mila kar padhein phir andar chaley gaey. phir iske baad nikley to maghrib aur isha mila kar padhein iske baad farmaya ke kal tum log agar Allah Taala ne chaha to Tabook ke chashmey par pahunchogey aur din nikalney se pahley nahi pahunch sakogey aur jo koi tum mein se us chashmey ke paas jaey, to uske pani ko hath na lagaey jab tak main na aaun. saiyedna Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke phir ham us chashmey par pahunchey aur ham se pahley wahan 2 aadmi pahunch gaey they. chashme ke pani ka ye haal tha ke jooti ke tasme ke barabar hoga, wo bhi ahista-ahista beh raha tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un donon aadmiyon se puchha ke tum ne iske pani mein hath lagaya? unhon-ne kaha ke haan, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko bura kaha (is liye ke unhon-ne hukm ke khilaf kya tha) aur Allah Taala ko jo manzoor tha wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko sunaya. phir logon ne chulluon se thoda thoda pani aik bartan mein jama kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne donon hath aur munh usmein dhoya, phir wo pani us chashme mein daal diya to wo chashma josh mar kar behney laga aur logon ne (apne janwaron aur aadmiyon ko) pani pilaana shuru kya. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey Muaz! agar teri zindagi rahi to to dekhega ke yahan jo jagah hai wo ghaney baghaat se lahlaha uthegi."
6346,"Sulaiman-bin-Bilal ne Amr-bin-Yahya se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abbas bin Sahal-bin-Sad Saaidi se, unhon-ne abu Humaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : saiyedna abu-Humaid (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Tabook ki jang (jange-Tabook) mein ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley. wadi-ul-Qura (Sham (Syria) ke rastey mein Madina se teen meel ke faasley par aik maqam hai) main aik aurat ke baagh ke paas pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke andaza lagaao us baagh mein kitna mewa hai? ham ne andaza kya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke andaazey mein wo das wasq malum hua. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us aurat se farmaya ke jab tak ham lot kar aaein tum ye (andaza) ginti yad rakhna, agar Allah ne chaha. phir ham log aagey chaley, yahan tak ke Tabook mein pahunchey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aaj raat tez aandhi chalegi, lihaza koi shakhs khada na ho aur jiske paas oont ho, wo usko mazbooti se baandh ley. phir aisa hi hua ke zordaar aandhi chali. aik shakhs khada hua to usko hua uda ley gaee, aur) wadi ( tay ke donon pahadon ke darmyan daal diya. Hakim ibne-Alma Ela ka eilchii aik khat lekar aaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye aik safaid khachchar tohfa laya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko jawab likha aur aik chadar tohfa bheji. phir ham lautey, yahan tak ke wadi-ul-Qura main pahunchey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us aurat se baagh ke mewey ka haal puchha ke kitna nikla? usne kaha pura das wasq nikla. ( phir (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main jaldi jaunga, lihaza tum mein se jiska dil chahey wo mere sath jaldi chaley aur jiska dil chahey thahar jaey. ham nikley yahan tak ke Madina dikhai diye laga, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye '' taaba'' hai (taaba Madina Munawra ka naam hai) aur ye Uhud pahaad hai jo ham ko chahta hai aur ham usko chahtey hain. phir farmaya ke Ansar ke gharon mein bani najjaar ke ghar behtreen hain (kyonke wo sabse pahley musalman huey) phir bani abdul-Ashhal ke ghar, phir bani Haris bin khazraj ke ghar. phir bani Saaida ke ghar aur Ansar ke sab gharon mein behtri hai. phir Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ham se miley. abu-Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke tum ne nahi suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar ke gharon ki behtri bayan farmai to ham ko sab ke akheer mein kar diya ? . ye sun kar saiyedna Sad (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se miley aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! aap ne Ansar ki fazeelat bayan ki aur hamko sabse aakhir mein kar diya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya tumko ye kafi nahi hai ke tum khair w barkat walon mein se ho jao?"
6347,"Sulaiman-bin-Bilal ne Amr-bin-Yahya se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abbas bin Sahal-bin-Sad Saaidi se, unhon-ne abu Humaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : saiyedna abu-Humaid (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Tabook ki jang (jange-Tabook) mein ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley. wadi-ul-Qura (Sham (Syria) ke rastey mein Madina se teen meel ke faasley par aik maqam hai) main aik aurat ke baagh ke paas pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke andaza lagaao us baagh mein kitna mewa hai? ham ne andaza kya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke andaazey mein wo das wasq malum hua. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us aurat se farmaya ke jab tak ham lot kar aaein tum ye (andaza) ginti yad rakhna, agar Allah ne chaha. phir ham log aagey chaley, yahan tak ke Tabook mein pahunchey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aaj raat tez aandhi chalegi, lihaza koi shakhs khada na ho aur jiske paas oont ho, wo usko mazbooti se baandh ley. phir aisa hi hua ke zordaar aandhi chali. aik shakhs khada hua to usko hua uda ley gaee, aur) wadi ( tay ke donon pahadon ke darmyan daal diya. Hakim ibne-Alma Ela ka eilchii aik khat lekar aaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye aik safaid khachchar tohfa laya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko jawab likha aur aik chadar tohfa bheji. phir ham lautey, yahan tak ke wadi-ul-Qura main pahunchey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us aurat se baagh ke mewey ka haal puchha ke kitna nikla? usne kaha pura das wasq nikla. ( phir (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main jaldi jaunga, lihaza tum mein se jiska dil chahey wo mere sath jaldi chaley aur jiska dil chahey thahar jaey. ham nikley yahan tak ke Madina dikhai diye laga, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye '' taaba'' hai (taaba Madina Munawra ka naam hai) aur ye Uhud pahaad hai jo ham ko chahta hai aur ham usko chahtey hain. phir farmaya ke Ansar ke gharon mein bani najjaar ke ghar behtreen hain (kyonke wo sabse pahley musalman huey) phir bani abdul-Ashhal ke ghar, phir bani Haris bin khazraj ke ghar. phir bani Saaida ke ghar aur Ansar ke sab gharon mein behtri hai. phir Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ham se miley. abu-Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke tum ne nahi suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar ke gharon ki behtri bayan farmai to ham ko sab ke akheer mein kar diya ? . ye sun kar saiyedna Sad (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se miley aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! aap ne Ansar ki fazeelat bayan ki aur hamko sabse aakhir mein kar diya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya tumko ye kafi nahi hai ke tum khair w barkat walon mein se ho jao?"
6348,"Affaan aur Mughira bin Salma makhzumi donon ne kaha : hamein Wuhaib ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Amr-bin-Yahya ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us farman tak : aur Ansar ke tamam gharon mein khair w barkat hai. unhon-ne Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ka qissa, jo uske baad hai, zikr nahi kya aur Wuhaib ki hadis mein mazeed ye bayan kya : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un logon ka Sara ilaqa (bataur hakim) usko likh diya, neez Wuhaib ki hadis mein ye zikr nahi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski taraf khat likha."
6349,"Affaan aur Mughira bin Salma makhzumi donon ne kaha : hamein Wuhaib ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Amr-bin-Yahya ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us farman tak : aur Ansar ke tamam gharon mein khair w barkat hai. unhon-ne Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ka qissa, jo uske baad hai, zikr nahi kya aur Wuhaib ki hadis mein mazeed ye bayan kya : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un logon ka Sara ilaqa (bataur hakim) usko likh diya, neez Wuhaib ki hadis mein ye zikr nahi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski taraf khat likha."
6350,"Mamar ne Zohri se, unhon-ne abu-Salma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, neez Muhammad-bin-Jafar bin Ziyad ne. alfaz unhi ke hain. Ibrahim bin Sad se, unhon-ne Sanan bin abi Sanan dauli se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Najad ki taraf jihad ko gaey to ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik wadi mein paya jahan kaantedaar darakht bahut zyada they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik darakht ke nichey utrey aur apni talwaar aik shaakh se latka di aur log us wadi mein alag-alag ho kar saaya dhoondhtey huey phail gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik shakhs mere paas aaya, main so raha tha ke usne talwaar utaar li aur main jaaga to wo mere sar par khada hua tha. mujhey us waqt khabar hui jab uske hath mein nangi talwaar aa gaee thi. wo bola ke ab tumhen mujh se kon bacha sakta hai? maine kaha ke Allah ! phir dusri baar usne yahi kaha to maine kaha ke Allah taalaa. ye sun kar us ne talwaar niyaam mein kar li. wo shakhs ye betha hai. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se kuchh bhi na kaha."
6351,"Mamar ne Zohri se, unhon-ne abu-Salma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, neez Muhammad-bin-Jafar bin Ziyad ne. alfaz unhi ke hain. Ibrahim bin Sad se, unhon-ne Sanan bin abi Sanan dauli se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Najad ki taraf jihad ko gaey to ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik wadi mein paya jahan kaantedaar darakht bahut zyada they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik darakht ke nichey utrey aur apni talwaar aik shaakh se latka di aur log us wadi mein alag-alag ho kar saaya dhoondhtey huey phail gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik shakhs mere paas aaya, main so raha tha ke usne talwaar utaar li aur main jaaga to wo mere sar par khada hua tha. mujhey us waqt khabar hui jab uske hath mein nangi talwaar aa gaee thi. wo bola ke ab tumhen mujh se kon bacha sakta hai? maine kaha ke Allah ! phir dusri baar usne yahi kaha to maine kaha ke Allah taalaa. ye sun kar us ne talwaar niyaam mein kar li. wo shakhs ye betha hai. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se kuchh bhi na kaha."
6352,"Shuaib ne Zohri se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Sanan bin abi Sanan dauli aur abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne, jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba mein se hain, un donon ko khabar di ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Najad ki taraf aik jang mein hissey liya. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas huey to wo bhi aap ke sath wapas huey, aik din do-pahar ke aaraam ka waqt ho gaya, iske baad unhon-ne Ibrahim bin Sad aur Mamar ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya."
6353,"Shuaib ne Zohri se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Sanan bin abi Sanan dauli aur abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne, jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba mein se hain, un donon ko khabar di ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Najad ki taraf aik jang mein hissey liya. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas huey to wo bhi aap ke sath wapas huey, aik din do-pahar ke aaraam ka waqt ho gaya, iske baad unhon-ne Ibrahim bin Sad aur Mamar ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya."
6354,"Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ( wapas ( aaey, yahan tak ke jab ham zaatur-Riqaa pahunchey, ( phir ( Zohri ki hadis ke ham mana riwayat ki aur ye nahi kaha : phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se koi taruz na farmaya,"
6355,"Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ( wapas ( aaey, yahan tak ke jab ham zaatur-Riqaa pahunchey, ( phir ( Zohri ki hadis ke ham mana riwayat ki aur ye nahi kaha : phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se koi taruz na farmaya,"
6356,"saiyedna abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : uski misal jo Allah ne mujhey hidayat aur ilm diya, aisi hai jaisey zamin par barish barsi aur us (zameen) mein kuchh hissey aisa tha jisne pani ko choos liya aur chaara aur bahut sa sabza ugaaya aur uska kuchh hissey sakht tha, usne pani ko jama rakha , phir Allah Taala ne us (pani) se logon ko fayda pahunchaya ke unhon-ne usmein se piyaa , pilaya aur churaaya aur uska kuchh hissey chatiyal maidan hai ke na to pani ko rokey aur na ghaas ugaaey .) jaisey chikni chattaan ke pani laga aur chal diya) to ye uski misal hai ke jisne Allah ke Deen ko samjha aur Allah ne usko us cheez se fayda diya jo mujhey ata farmai, us ne aap bhi jana aur dusron ko bhi sikhaya aur jisne us taraf sar na uthaya (yani tawajjoh na ki) aur Allah ki hidayat ko jis ko main de kar bheja gaya qabool na kya."
6357,"saiyedna abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : uski misal jo Allah ne mujhey hidayat aur ilm diya, aisi hai jaisey zamin par barish barsi aur us (zameen) mein kuchh hissey aisa tha jisne pani ko choos liya aur chaara aur bahut sa sabza ugaaya aur uska kuchh hissey sakht tha, usne pani ko jama rakha , phir Allah Taala ne us (pani) se logon ko fayda pahunchaya ke unhon-ne usmein se piyaa , pilaya aur churaaya aur uska kuchh hissey chatiyal maidan hai ke na to pani ko rokey aur na ghaas ugaaey .) jaisey chikni chattaan ke pani laga aur chal diya) to ye uski misal hai ke jisne Allah ke Deen ko samjha aur Allah ne usko us cheez se fayda diya jo mujhey ata farmai, us ne aap bhi jana aur dusron ko bhi sikhaya aur jisne us taraf sar na uthaya (yani tawajjoh na ki) aur Allah ki hidayat ko jis ko main de kar bheja gaya qabool na kya."
6358,"saiyedna abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri misal aur mere Deen ki misal jo ke Allah ne mujhey de kar bheja hai, aisi hai jaisey us shakhs ki misal jo apni qaum ke paas aaya aur kehney laga ke aey meri qaum ! maine lashkar ko apni donon aankhon se dekha hai (yani dushman ki fauj ko) aur main saaf-saaf daraane wala hun, to jaldi bhaago. ab uski qaum mein se kuchh ne uska kehna maana aur wo Sham (Syria) hotey hi bhag gaey aur aaraam se chaley gaey aur kuchh ne jhutlaya aur wo subah tak us thikaaney mein rahe aur subah hotey hi lashkar un par toot pada aur unko tabah kya aur jad se ukhed diya. to yahi us shakhs ki misal hai jisne meri itaat ki aur jo kuchh mein lekar aaya hun uski ittaba (pairvi) ki aur jisne mera kehna na maana aur sachey Deen ko jhutlaaya."
6359,"saiyedna abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri misal aur mere Deen ki misal jo ke Allah ne mujhey de kar bheja hai, aisi hai jaisey us shakhs ki misal jo apni qaum ke paas aaya aur kehney laga ke aey meri qaum ! maine lashkar ko apni donon aankhon se dekha hai (yani dushman ki fauj ko) aur main saaf-saaf daraane wala hun, to jaldi bhaago. ab uski qaum mein se kuchh ne uska kehna maana aur wo Sham (Syria) hotey hi bhag gaey aur aaraam se chaley gaey aur kuchh ne jhutlaya aur wo subah tak us thikaaney mein rahe aur subah hotey hi lashkar un par toot pada aur unko tabah kya aur jad se ukhed diya. to yahi us shakhs ki misal hai jisne meri itaat ki aur jo kuchh mein lekar aaya hun uski ittaba (pairvi) ki aur jisne mera kehna na maana aur sachey Deen ko jhutlaaya."
6360,"Mughira bin Abdur-Rehman qarshi ne hamein abu Zinad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Aaraj se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri aur meri ummat ki misal us shakhs ki tarah hai jisne aag roshan ki to hashraatul-arz aur patingey us aag mein girney lagey. to main tum ko kamar se pakad kar rokney wala hun aur tum zabardasti usmein girtey ja rahe ho."
6361,"Mughira bin Abdur-Rehman qarshi ne hamein abu Zinad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Aaraj se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri aur meri ummat ki misal us shakhs ki tarah hai jisne aag roshan ki to hashraatul-arz aur patingey us aag mein girney lagey. to main tum ko kamar se pakad kar rokney wala hun aur tum zabardasti usmein girtey ja rahe ho."
6362,Sufiyan ne abu Zinad se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
6363,Sufiyan ne abu Zinad se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
6364,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin. unhon-ne kai hadisein bayan kin, unmein se aik ye hai : aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ke meri misal us shakhs ki si hai jisne aag jalaai, jab uske gird roshni hui to usmein keedey aur ye janwar jo aag mein hain, girney lagey aur wo shakhs unko rokney laga, lekin wo na rukey aur is mein girney lagey. ye misal hai meri aur tumhari, main tumhari kamar se pakad kar jahannam se rokta hun aur kehta hun ke jahannam ke paas se chaley aao aur tum nahi mantey usi mein ghusey jatey ho."
6365,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin. unhon-ne kai hadisein bayan kin, unmein se aik ye hai : aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ke meri misal us shakhs ki si hai jisne aag jalaai, jab uske gird roshni hui to usmein keedey aur ye janwar jo aag mein hain, girney lagey aur wo shakhs unko rokney laga, lekin wo na rukey aur is mein girney lagey. ye misal hai meri aur tumhari, main tumhari kamar se pakad kar jahannam se rokta hun aur kehta hun ke jahannam ke paas se chaley aao aur tum nahi mantey usi mein ghusey jatey ho."
6366,"Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri aur tumhari misal us shakhs jaisi hai jisne aag jalaai to makdey aur patingey usmein girney lagey. wo shakhs hai ke unko us se rok raha hai, main tumhari kamron par pakad kar tumhen aag se hata raha hun aur tum ho ke mere hathon se nikley ja rahe ho."
6367,"Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri aur tumhari misal us shakhs jaisi hai jisne aag jalaai to makdey aur patingey usmein girney lagey. wo shakhs hai ke unko us se rok raha hai, main tumhari kamron par pakad kar tumhen aag se hata raha hun aur tum ho ke mere hathon se nikley ja rahe ho."
6368,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri aur doosrey paighambaron ki misal jo ke mere se pahley ho chukey hain, aisi hai jaisey kisi shakhs ne ghar banaya aur uski zebaaish aur aaraaish ki, lekin uske konon mein se aik koney mein aik ent ki jagah chhod di to log iske gird phir ne lagey aur unhein wo Imaarat pasand aai aur wo kehney lagey ke ye tu ney aik ent yahan kyon na rakh di? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main wo ent hun."
6369,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri aur doosrey paighambaron ki misal jo ke mere se pahley ho chukey hain, aisi hai jaisey kisi shakhs ne ghar banaya aur uski zebaaish aur aaraaish ki, lekin uske konon mein se aik koney mein aik ent ki jagah chhod di to log iske gird phir ne lagey aur unhein wo Imaarat pasand aai aur wo kehney lagey ke ye tu ney aik ent yahan kyon na rakh di? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main wo ent hun."
6370,"Mamar ne hamein Hammam-bin-Munabba se hadis bayan ki, kaha : ye ( hadisein ( hamein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, unhon-ne kai hadisein bayan kin, unmein se aik ye hai ke abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri aur mujh se pahley anbiya (Alaihissalam) ki misal us shakhs ki tarah hai jisne (eik Imaarat mein) kai ghar banaey. unhein bahut achchha , bahut khoobsurat banaya aur uske konon mein se aik koney mein, aik eent ki jagah ke siwa us ( poori Imaarat ( ko achi tarah mukammal kar diya. log iske ird-gird ghoomney lagey wo Imaarat unhein bahut achi lagti aur wo kehtey : aap ne is jagah aik eent kyon na laga di taake tumhari Imaarat mukammal ho jati. to Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main hi wo eent tha (jiske lag janey ke baad wo Imaarat mukammal ho gaee.)"
