6382,"hamein Zayda ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein abdul-Muttalib-bin-Umair ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Jundub-bin-Abdullah bijli (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke maine Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : main hauz par tumhara peshrau hun."
6383,"hamein Zayda ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein abdul-Muttalib-bin-Umair ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Jundub-bin-Abdullah bijli (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke maine Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : main hauz par tumhara peshrau hun."
6384,"Misar aur Shoba donon ne abdul-Malik-bin-Umair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske jaisi riwayat ki."
6385,"Misar aur Shoba donon ne abdul-Malik-bin-Umair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske jaisi riwayat ki."
6386,"Yaqoob-bin-Abdur-Rehman-al-qaari ne abu-Hazim se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) (ibne-Sad Saaidi) se suna, keh rahe they : maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they : main tum se pahley apne hauz par pahunchne wala hun. jo us hauz par peeney ke liye aa jaeyga, pi lega aur jo pi lega wo kabhi piyaasa nahi hoga. mere paas bahut se log aaeingey. main unhein janta hoonga. wo mujhey jantey hongey. phir mere aur unke darmyan rukaawat haail kar di jaeygi. abu-Hazim ne kaha : main ye hadis ( sunney walon ko) suna raha tha ke Nauman-bin-abi-Ayash ne bhi ye hadis suni to kehney lagey : aap ne Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ko isi tarah kehtey huey suna hai? maine kaha : ji haan."
6387,"Yaqoob-bin-Abdur-Rehman-al-qaari ne abu-Hazim se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) (ibne-Sad Saaidi) se suna, keh rahe they : maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they : main tum se pahley apne hauz par pahunchne wala hun. jo us hauz par peeney ke liye aa jaeyga, pi lega aur jo pi lega wo kabhi piyaasa nahi hoga. mere paas bahut se log aaeingey. main unhein janta hoonga. wo mujhey jantey hongey. phir mere aur unke darmyan rukaawat haail kar di jaeygi. abu-Hazim ne kaha : main ye hadis ( sunney walon ko) suna raha tha ke Nauman-bin-abi-Ayash ne bhi ye hadis suni to kehney lagey : aap ne Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ko isi tarah kehtey huey suna hai? maine kaha : ji haan."
6388,"unhon ( Nauman bin abi Ayash ( ne kaha : aur main gawahi deta hun ke maine Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo us ( hadis) mein mazeed ye bayan kartey they ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaaengey : ye mere (log) hain to kaha jaeyga : aap nahi jantey ke unhon-ne aap ke baad kya kya. to main kahunga : doori ho, halaakat ho ! unke liye jinhoney mere baad) Deen mein) tabdili kar di."
6389,"unhon ( Nauman bin abi Ayash ( ne kaha : aur main gawahi deta hun ke maine Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo us ( hadis) mein mazeed ye bayan kartey they ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaaengey : ye mere (log) hain to kaha jaeyga : aap nahi jantey ke unhon-ne aap ke baad kya kya. to main kahunga : doori ho, halaakat ho ! unke liye jinhoney mere baad) Deen mein) tabdili kar di."
6390,"abu-Usama ne abu-Hazim se, unhon-ne Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aur (doosri sanad ke sath abu-Hazim ne) Nauman-bin-abi-Ayash se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Yaqoob (bin-Abdur-Rehman-al-qaari) ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
6391,"abu-Usama ne abu-Hazim se, unhon-ne Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aur (doosri sanad ke sath abu-Hazim ne) Nauman-bin-abi-Ayash se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Yaqoob (bin-Abdur-Rehman-al-qaari) ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
6392,"Naafe bin umr jamhi ne ibne-abi-Mulaika se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mera hoz (lambai chaudai mein) aik maah ki masafat ke barabar hai aur uske (charon) kinarey barabar hain (murabba hai), iska pani chandi se zyada chamakdaar, aur uski khushbu kastoori se zyada muattar hai, iske koozey aasman ke sitaron jitney hain. jo shakhs usmein se pi lega, usey uske baad kabhi piyaas nahi lageygi."
6393,"Naafe bin umr jamhi ne ibne-abi-Mulaika se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mera hoz (lambai chaudai mein) aik maah ki masafat ke barabar hai aur uske (charon) kinarey barabar hain (murabba hai), iska pani chandi se zyada chamakdaar, aur uski khushbu kastoori se zyada muattar hai, iske koozey aasman ke sitaron jitney hain. jo shakhs usmein se pi lega, usey uske baad kabhi piyaas nahi lageygi."
6394,"Hazrat Asma binte-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : hoz mein (maujood) mein hunga taake dekhun ke tum mein se kon mere paas aata hai, kuchh logon ko mujh (tak pahunchne) se pahley hi pakad liya jaeyga to main kahunga : aey mere rab! ye mere hain meri ummat mein se hain. to kaha jaeyga, aapko malum nahi ke aap ke baad unhon-ne kya ( kuchh) kiya? aap ke baad unhon-ne apni eidiyon par wapas ghoomney mein (zara) der nahi ki. (Naafe ne) kaha : ibne-abi-Mulaika ye dua kartey they : aey Allah! ham is baat se teri panah mein aatey hain ke ham apni eidiyon par palat jayen ya hamein kisi aazmaish mein daal kar apne Deen se hata diya jaey."
6395,"Hazrat Asma binte-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : hoz mein (maujood) mein hunga taake dekhun ke tum mein se kon mere paas aata hai, kuchh logon ko mujh (tak pahunchne) se pahley hi pakad liya jaeyga to main kahunga : aey mere rab! ye mere hain meri ummat mein se hain. to kaha jaeyga, aapko malum nahi ke aap ke baad unhon-ne kya ( kuchh) kiya? aap ke baad unhon-ne apni eidiyon par wapas ghoomney mein (zara) der nahi ki. (Naafe ne) kaha : ibne-abi-Mulaika ye dua kartey they : aey Allah! ham is baat se teri panah mein aatey hain ke ham apni eidiyon par palat jayen ya hamein kisi aazmaish mein daal kar apne Deen se hata diya jaey."
6396,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ke sath they aur farma rahe they : main hauz par hunga. intizar kar raha hunga ke mere paas peeney ke liye kon aata hai. Allah ki qasam! mujh (tak pahunchne) se pahley kuchh logon ko kaat (kar alag kar) diya jaeyga, to main kahunga : mere rab! (ye ( mere hain meri ummat mein se hain. to Allah Taala farmaeyga, aap nahi jantey ke unhon-ne aap ke baad kya kya? ye musalsal apni eidiyon par palat-tey rahe."
6397,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ke sath they aur farma rahe they : main hauz par hunga. intizar kar raha hunga ke mere paas peeney ke liye kon aata hai. Allah ki qasam! mujh (tak pahunchne) se pahley kuchh logon ko kaat (kar alag kar) diya jaeyga, to main kahunga : mere rab! (ye ( mere hain meri ummat mein se hain. to Allah Taala farmaeyga, aap nahi jantey ke unhon-ne aap ke baad kya kya? ye musalsal apni eidiyon par palat-tey rahe."
6398,"Bukair ne Qasim bin Abbas Hashmi se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke Maula Ubaidullah bin Raafe se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : main logon se sunti thi ke wo hauz ( kausar (ka zikr kartey they. maine ye baat khud Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se nahi suni thi, phir un ( meri baari ke) dinon mein se aik din hua aur khadima meri kanghi kar rahi thi ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye kehtey huey suna : aey logo! maine khaadima se kaha : mujh se peechhey hat jao! wo kehney lagi, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mardon ko pukara (mukhaatab farmaya) hai aurton ko nahi. maine kaha : main bhi logon mein se hun (sirf mard hi log nahi hotey) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main hauz par tumhara pesh ro hunga. mere paas tum mein se koi is tarah na aaey ke usey mujh se door dhakela ja raha ho, jis tarah bhatkey huey oont ko (rewad se) aur door dhakela jata hai. main poochhunga. ye kis wjah se ho raha hai? to kaha jaeyga aap nahi jantey ke unhon-ne aap ke baad (deen mein) kya naey kaam nikaley they. to main kahunga doori ho!"
