6402,"Leis ne Yazeed bin abi Habib se, unhon-ne Abul-Khair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif le gaey aur ahal ahad par isi tarah namaaze-janaaza padhi, jis tarah maiyat par padhi jati hai, phir aap palat kar member par tashrif farma huey aur farmaya : main hauz par tumhara pesh-ro hunga aur main tum par gawahi dene wala hunga aur mein, Allah ki qasam! jaisey ab bhi apne hauz ko dekh raha hun. mujhey zamin ke khazaanon ki chaabiyan ya ( farmaya : ( zamin ki chaabiyan ata ki gain aur Allah ki qasam! main tumharey barey mein is baat se nahi darta ke mere baad tum shirk karogey. lekin main is baat se darta hun ke tum un (khazaanon ke mamley) mein aik-doosrey ke sath muqaabla karogey (ke unmein se kon zyada fayda uthata aur zyada daulat mandi ka muzaahira karta hai.)"
