6404,"saiyedna Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Uhud ke shaheedon par Namaz padhi phir member par chadhey jaisey koi rukhsat karta hai zindon aur mardon ko aur farmaya : ''main tumhara pesh khema hunga hauz par aur us hauz ki chaudai itni hai jaisey Ela se Johfa (ye donon maqam ke naam hain Ela Madina se pandarah manzil par aur Johfa saat (7) manzil par hai) mujhey ye dar nahi ke tum mere baad mushrik ho jaogey lekin main dara ke duniya ke laalach mein pad kar aapas mein ladney na lago, phir tabah ho jao jaisey tum se pahley log tabah huey.'' Aqba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye aakhiri baar mera dekhna tha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko member par."
