6414,"ibne-abi Adi ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Mabad bin Khalid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Harisa (bin Wahab Khuzai ( (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, ke unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap ne farmaya : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka hauz ( itna chaudaa hai) jitna sanaa aur Madina ke darmyan (ka fasla ( hai. mustaurid ( ibne-Shaddad ( (Raziallahu anhu) ne un (Hazrat Harisa (Raziallahu anhu)) se kaha : aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se nahi suna, ke aap ne farmaya : bartan ? unhon-ne kaha : nahi to mustaurid (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : usmein bartan sitaron ki tarah nazar aaeingey."
6415,"ibne-abi Adi ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Mabad bin Khalid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Harisa (bin Wahab Khuzai ( (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, ke unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap ne farmaya : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka hauz ( itna chaudaa hai) jitna sanaa aur Madina ke darmyan (ka fasla ( hai. mustaurid ( ibne-Shaddad ( (Raziallahu anhu) ne un (Hazrat Harisa (Raziallahu anhu)) se kaha : aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se nahi suna, ke aap ne farmaya : bartan ? unhon-ne kaha : nahi to mustaurid (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : usmein bartan sitaron ki tarah nazar aaeingey."
6416,"Harmi bin Umara ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Mabad bin Khalid se hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Harisa bin Wahab Khuzai (Raziallahu anhu) ko suna wo keh rahe they ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna aur unhon-ne (Harmi bin Umara) ne hauz ka zikr kya, usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah. unhon-ne Hazrat mustaurid aur un (hazrat Harisa (Raziallahu anhu)) ka qaul zikr nahi kya."
6417,"Harmi bin Umara ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Mabad bin Khalid se hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Harisa bin Wahab Khuzai (Raziallahu anhu) ko suna wo keh rahe they ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna aur unhon-ne (Harmi bin Umara) ne hauz ka zikr kya, usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah. unhon-ne Hazrat mustaurid aur un (hazrat Harisa (Raziallahu anhu)) ka qaul zikr nahi kya."
6418,"Ayub ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumharey aagey (jis manzil ki taraf tum ja rahe ho ( hauz hai uske 2 kinaron ke darmyan jarbaa aur azruh (Sham (Syria) aur Palestine ke 2 maqam) ke darmyan jitna fasla hai."
6419,"Ayub ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumharey aagey (jis manzil ki taraf tum ja rahe ho ( hauz hai uske 2 kinaron ke darmyan jarbaa aur azruh (Sham (Syria) aur Palestine ke 2 maqam) ke darmyan jitna fasla hai."
6420,"Zuhair-bin-Harab Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur Ubaidullah bin Saeed ne kaha : hamein Yahya qattaan ne Ubaidullah se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, ke aap ne farmaya : tumharey aagey hauz hai (uski wusat itni hai jitna) jarbaa aur azrah ke darmyan ka fasla hai. aur ibne-Musanna ki riwayat mein mera hauz ke alfaz hain."
6421,"Zuhair-bin-Harab Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur Ubaidullah bin Saeed ne kaha : hamein Yahya qattaan ne Ubaidullah se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, ke aap ne farmaya : tumharey aagey hauz hai (uski wusat itni hai jitna) jarbaa aur azrah ke darmyan ka fasla hai. aur ibne-Musanna ki riwayat mein mera hauz ke alfaz hain."
6422,Abdullah-bin-Numair aur Muhammad-bin-Bishr ne kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki manind (tarah) riwayat ki aur mazeed bayan kya ke Ubaidullah ne kaha : maine un (Naafe) se puchha to unhon-ne kaha : Sham (Syria) ki 2 bastiyan hain unke darmyan teen raaton ki masafat hai. ibne-Bishr ki riwayat mein teen din (ka zikr) hai.
6423,Abdullah-bin-Numair aur Muhammad-bin-Bishr ne kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki manind (tarah) riwayat ki aur mazeed bayan kya ke Ubaidullah ne kaha : maine un (Naafe) se puchha to unhon-ne kaha : Sham (Syria) ki 2 bastiyan hain unke darmyan teen raaton ki masafat hai. ibne-Bishr ki riwayat mein teen din (ka zikr) hai.
6424,"Musa-bin-Aqba ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Ubaidullah ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
6425,"Musa-bin-Aqba ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Ubaidullah ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
6426,"Umar-bin Muhammad ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin umr (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tumharey samney aisa hauz hai jitna jarbaa aur azruh ke darmyan ki masafat hai is mein aasman ke sitaron jitney koozey hain jo us tak pahunchega aur is mein se piyega wo iske baad kabhi piyaasa nahi hoga."
6427,"Umar-bin Muhammad ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin umr (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tumharey samney aisa hauz hai jitna jarbaa aur azruh ke darmyan ki masafat hai is mein aasman ke sitaron jitney koozey hain jo us tak pahunchega aur is mein se piyega wo iske baad kabhi piyaasa nahi hoga."
6428,Abdullah-bin Samit ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : maine puchha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hauz ke bartan kaisey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jaan hai! us hauz ke bartan aasman ke chhotey aur badey (tamam sitaron ki tadaad se zyada hain. yad rakho ! jo andheri saaf matle ki raat mein hotey hain. wo jannat ke bartan hain ke jo unse (sharab kosar) pi lega wo apne zimmey ( jannat mein janey ke dauraaniye) ke aakhir tak kabhi piyasa nahi hoga. usmein jannat (ki baarane-rehmat) ke 2 par naley aakar girtey hain jo usmein se pi lega wo kabhi piyaasa nahi hoga. uski chaudai uski lambai ke barabar hai jaisey amman se Ela tak (ka fasla) hai. uska pani doodh se zyada safaid aur shehad se zyada meetha hai.
6429,Abdullah-bin Samit ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : maine puchha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hauz ke bartan kaisey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jaan hai! us hauz ke bartan aasman ke chhotey aur badey (tamam sitaron ki tadaad se zyada hain. yad rakho ! jo andheri saaf matle ki raat mein hotey hain. wo jannat ke bartan hain ke jo unse (sharab kosar) pi lega wo apne zimmey ( jannat mein janey ke dauraaniye) ke aakhir tak kabhi piyasa nahi hoga. usmein jannat (ki baarane-rehmat) ke 2 par naley aakar girtey hain jo usmein se pi lega wo kabhi piyaasa nahi hoga. uski chaudai uski lambai ke barabar hai jaisey amman se Ela tak (ka fasla) hai. uska pani doodh se zyada safaid aur shehad se zyada meetha hai.
6430,"Hisham ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Saalim-bin abi Jaad se, unhon-ne Madaan bin abi Talha Yamari se, unhon-ne Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main apne hauz par peeney ki jagah se ahale-Yaman (Ansar aslan Yaman se they) ke liye logon ko hataaunga. main (apne hauz ke pani par) apni lathi maarunga to wo un par behney lagega. aap se us ( hauz ( ki chaudai ke barey mein puchha gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mere khadey honey ki (is) jagah se Amman tak aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us (hauz) ke mashroob ke barey mein puchha gaya to farmaya : wo doodh se zyada safaid aur shehad se zyada meetha hai, jannat se 2 parnaley usmein tezi se shamil ho kar usmein izafa kartey rahtey hain. unmein se aik parnaala soney ka hai aur aik chandi kaa."
6431,"Hisham ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Saalim-bin abi Jaad se, unhon-ne Madaan bin abi Talha Yamari se, unhon-ne Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main apne hauz par peeney ki jagah se ahale-Yaman (Ansar aslan Yaman se they) ke liye logon ko hataaunga. main (apne hauz ke pani par) apni lathi maarunga to wo un par behney lagega. aap se us ( hauz ( ki chaudai ke barey mein puchha gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mere khadey honey ki (is) jagah se Amman tak aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us (hauz) ke mashroob ke barey mein puchha gaya to farmaya : wo doodh se zyada safaid aur shehad se zyada meetha hai, jannat se 2 parnaley usmein tezi se shamil ho kar usmein izafa kartey rahtey hain. unmein se aik parnaala soney ka hai aur aik chandi kaa."
6432,"Sheban ne Qatada se Hisham ki sanad ke sath uski hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki, magar us ne is tarah kaha : main qiyamat ke din hauz ke pani peeney ki jagah par hoonga."
6433,"Sheban ne Qatada se Hisham ki sanad ke sath uski hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki, magar us ne is tarah kaha : main qiyamat ke din hauz ke pani peeney ki jagah par hoonga."
6434,"Muhammad-bin Bishr ne kaha : hamein Yahya bin Hammad ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Qatada se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Saalim-bin abi Jaad se, unhon-ne Madaan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hauz ki hadis riwayat ki, maine Yahya bin Hammad se kaha : ye hadis aap ne abu-Awana se suni hai? to unhon-ne kaha : aur Shoba se bhi suni hai. maine kaha : meri khaatir usmein nigaah ( bhi) daalein . (aap ke saheefey mein jahan likhi hui hai usey bhi padh lein) unhon-ne meri khaatir usmein nazar ki (usey padha) aur mujhey wo hadis bayan ki, (unki riwayat mein kisi bhool chook ka bhi imkan nahi.)"
6435,"Muhammad-bin Bishr ne kaha : hamein Yahya bin Hammad ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Qatada se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Saalim-bin abi Jaad se, unhon-ne Madaan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hauz ki hadis riwayat ki, maine Yahya bin Hammad se kaha : ye hadis aap ne abu-Awana se suni hai? to unhon-ne kaha : aur Shoba se bhi suni hai. maine kaha : meri khaatir usmein nigaah ( bhi) daalein . (aap ke saheefey mein jahan likhi hui hai usey bhi padh lein) unhon-ne meri khaatir usmein nazar ki (usey padha) aur mujhey wo hadis bayan ki, (unki riwayat mein kisi bhool chook ka bhi imkan nahi.)"
6436,"Rabe-bin-Muslim ne Muhammad-bin-Ziyad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main hauz se logon ko is tarah hataaunga jis tarah ajnabii oonton ko (apne ghaat se) hataya jata hai."
6437,"Rabe-bin-Muslim ne Muhammad-bin-Ziyad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main hauz se logon ko is tarah hataaunga jis tarah ajnabii oonton ko (apne ghaat se) hataya jata hai."
6438,"Shoba ne Muhammad-bin-Ziyad se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, usi ki tarah."
6439,"Shoba ne Muhammad-bin-Ziyad se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, usi ki tarah."
6440,ibne-Shahab se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mere hauz ki miqdar itni hai jitni ela aur Yaman ke sanaa ke darmyan doori hai aur uske bartanon ki tadaad aasman ke sitaron ki tarah hai.
6441,ibne-Shahab se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mere hauz ki miqdar itni hai jitni ela aur Yaman ke sanaa ke darmyan doori hai aur uske bartanon ki tadaad aasman ke sitaron ki tarah hai.
6442,"Abdul-Azeez bin Suheb ne kaha : hamein Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hauz par mere sathiyon mein se kuchh aadmi aaeingey yahan tak ke jab main unhein dekhunga aur unko mere samney kya jaeyga to unhein mujh (tak pahunchne) se pahley utha liya jaey, main zor de kar kahunga : aey mere rab! (ye) mere sathi hain mere sathi hain to mujh se kaha jaeyga aap nahi jantey ke unhon-ne aap ke baad kya nai baatein nikaalin."
6443,"Abdul-Azeez bin Suheb ne kaha : hamein Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hauz par mere sathiyon mein se kuchh aadmi aaeingey yahan tak ke jab main unhein dekhunga aur unko mere samney kya jaeyga to unhein mujh (tak pahunchne) se pahley utha liya jaey, main zor de kar kahunga : aey mere rab! (ye) mere sathi hain mere sathi hain to mujh se kaha jaeyga aap nahi jantey ke unhon-ne aap ke baad kya nai baatein nikaalin."
