6447,"Motamir ke walid Sulaiman ne kaha : hamein Qatada ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mere hauz ki 2 tarfon (donon kinaron) ke darmyan itna fasla hai jitna sanaa aur Madina ke darmyan hai."
6448,"Hisham aur abu-Awana donon ne Qatada se unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ke tarah riwaayat ki, magar un donon ne shak se kaam letey huey kaha : ya (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ( Madina aur Amman ke darmyan ki doori ki tarah (fasla hai) aur abu-Awana ki hadis mein ye alfaz hain. mere hauz ke donon kinaron ke darmyan ."
