6456,"Aamir bin Sad-bin-abi-Waqas ne kaha : maine apne ghulam Naafe ke hath Hazrat Jaabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) ko khat bheja ke aap mujhey koi aisi cheez bataein. jo aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni ho, unhon-ne mujhey (jawab mein) likha : maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna hai. main hauz par (tumhara) pesh-ro hunga."
