6458,"Misar ne Sad bin Ibrahim se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Uhud ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daain aur baain 2 aadmiyon ko dekha wo safaid libaas mein they, unko na maine us se pahley kabhi dekha tha na baad mein yani Hazrat Jibreel (Alaihissalam) aur Mikaail (Alaihissalam) ko."
6459,"Misar ne Sad bin Ibrahim se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Uhud ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daain aur baain 2 aadmiyon ko dekha wo safaid libaas mein they, unko na maine us se pahley kabhi dekha tha na baad mein yani Hazrat Jibreel (Alaihissalam) aur Mikaail (Alaihissalam) ko."
6460,"Ibrahim bin Sad ne kaha : hamein Sad ne apne walid (Ibrahim) se unhon-ne Hazrat Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Uhud ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daain aur baain safaid kapdon mein malboos 2 aadmi dekhey wo aap ki taraf se shiddat ke sath jang kar rahe they. maine unko na us se pahley dekha tha na baad mein kabhi dekha."
6461,"Ibrahim bin Sad ne kaha : hamein Sad ne apne walid (Ibrahim) se unhon-ne Hazrat Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Uhud ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daain aur baain safaid kapdon mein malboos 2 aadmi dekhey wo aap ki taraf se shiddat ke sath jang kar rahe they. maine unko na us se pahley dekha tha na baad mein kabhi dekha."
6462,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tamam insanon mein sabse badh kar khoobsurat sab insanon se badh kar data aur sabse zyada bahaadur they. aik raat Madina waaley (eik awaz sun kar) khof-zada ho gaey, sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) us awaz ki taraf gaey, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein us jagah se wapas aatey huey miley, aap sabse pahley awaz (ki jagah) tak pahunchey, aap Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghodey ki nangi peeth par Sawar they, aap ki gardan Mubarak mein talwaar latki hui thi aur aap farma rahe they. khof mein mubtala na ho khof mein mubtlaa na ho ( phir (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ham ne is (ghodey) ko samandar ki tarah paya hai ya ( farmaya ( wo to samandar hai. unhon ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : aur (is se pahley) wo sust raftaar ghoda tha."
6463,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tamam insanon mein sabse badh kar khoobsurat sab insanon se badh kar data aur sabse zyada bahaadur they. aik raat Madina waaley (eik awaz sun kar) khof-zada ho gaey, sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) us awaz ki taraf gaey, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein us jagah se wapas aatey huey miley, aap sabse pahley awaz (ki jagah) tak pahunchey, aap Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghodey ki nangi peeth par Sawar they, aap ki gardan Mubarak mein talwaar latki hui thi aur aap farma rahe they. khof mein mubtala na ho khof mein mubtlaa na ho ( phir (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ham ne is (ghodey) ko samandar ki tarah paya hai ya ( farmaya ( wo to samandar hai. unhon ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : aur (is se pahley) wo sust raftaar ghoda tha."
6464,"Wakee ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik baar Madina mein khof phail gaya Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ka aik ghoda udhar liya, usey mandoob kaha jata tha aap is par Sawar huey to aap ne farmaya : ham ne koi dar aur khof ki baat nahi dekhi aur is ghodey ko ham ne samandar (ki tarah) paya hai."
6465,"Wakee ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik baar Madina mein khof phail gaya Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ka aik ghoda udhar liya, usey mandoob kaha jata tha aap is par Sawar huey to aap ne farmaya : ham ne koi dar aur khof ki baat nahi dekhi aur is ghodey ko ham ne samandar (ki tarah) paya hai."
6466,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar aur Khalid-bin Haris ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, aur ibne-Jafar ki riwayat mein hai, unhon (Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : hamara ghoda aur unhon-ne ye nahi kaha ke abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ka (ghoda.) aur Khalid ki hadis mein hai. Qatada se riwayat hai, maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna."
6467,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar aur Khalid-bin Haris ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, aur ibne-Jafar ki riwayat mein hai, unhon (Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : hamara ghoda aur unhon-ne ye nahi kaha ke abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ka (ghoda.) aur Khalid ki hadis mein hai. Qatada se riwayat hai, maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna."
6468,"Ibrahim (bin Sad ( ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah-bin Utba-bin- Masood se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khair (achi chizon) mein tamam insanon mein se zyada data they. aur aap Ramazan ke mahiney mein sakhawat mein bahut hi zyada badh jatey they. Jibreel (Alaihissalam) har saal Ramazan ke mahiney mein iske khatm honey tak (rozaana aa kar) aap se miltey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke samney Quran Majeed ki qirat farmatey they. aur jab Hazrat Jibreel (Alaihissalam) aap se aa kar miltey they, to aap khair (ke ata karne) mein barish barsaney wali hawaaon se bhi zyada data ho jatey they."
6469,"Ibrahim (bin Sad ( ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah-bin Utba-bin- Masood se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khair (achi chizon) mein tamam insanon mein se zyada data they. aur aap Ramazan ke mahiney mein sakhawat mein bahut hi zyada badh jatey they. Jibreel (Alaihissalam) har saal Ramazan ke mahiney mein iske khatm honey tak (rozaana aa kar) aap se miltey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke samney Quran Majeed ki qirat farmatey they. aur jab Hazrat Jibreel (Alaihissalam) aap se aa kar miltey they, to aap khair (ke ata karne) mein barish barsaney wali hawaaon se bhi zyada data ho jatey they."
