6476,"hamein Abdul-Azeez ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey to Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne mera hath pakda aur mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein le gaey aur kaha : Allah ke rasool! Anas aik samajhdar ladka hai, isliye ye aap ki khidmat karega (Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : phir main safar aur hazar mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat karta raha Allah ki qism ! maine koi kaam kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye nahi farmaya : tum ne ye kaam is tarah kyon kiya? aur maine koi kaam na kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye nahi farmaya : tum ne ye kaam is tarah kyon nahi kiya?"
6477,"hamein Abdul-Azeez ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey to Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne mera hath pakda aur mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein le gaey aur kaha : Allah ke rasool! Anas aik samajhdar ladka hai, isliye ye aap ki khidmat karega (Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : phir main safar aur hazar mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat karta raha Allah ki qism ! maine koi kaam kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye nahi farmaya : tum ne ye kaam is tarah kyon kiya? aur maine koi kaam na kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye nahi farmaya : tum ne ye kaam is tarah kyon nahi kiya?"
6478,"Saeed bin abi burda ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine 9 saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat ki, mujhey ilm nahi ke aap ne kabhi mujh se yun farmaya ho tum ne is-is tarah kyon kiya? aur na Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi cheez mein kabhi mujh par nukta chaini ki."
6479,"Saeed bin abi burda ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine 9 saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat ki, mujhey ilm nahi ke aap ne kabhi mujh se yun farmaya ho tum ne is-is tarah kyon kiya? aur na Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi cheez mein kabhi mujh par nukta chaini ki."
6480,"Ishaq ne kaha : Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tamam insanon mein akhlaaq ke sabse achchhey they, aap ne aik din mujhey kisi kaam se bheja, maine kaha : Allah ki qism ! main nahi jaaunga. halanke mere dil mein ye tha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey jis kaam ka hukm diya hai main uske liye zaroor jaaunga. to main chala gaya yahan tak ke main chand ladkon ke paas se guzra, wo bazar mein khel rahe they, phir achcha (maine dekha) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne peechhey se meri guddi se mujhey pakad liya, maine aap ki taraf dekha to aap hans rahe they. aap ne farmaya : aey chhotey Anas ! kya tum wahan gaey they jahan ( janey ko) maine kaha tha? maine kaha ji haan , Allah ke rasool! mein ja raha hun."
6481,"Ishaq ne kaha : Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tamam insanon mein akhlaaq ke sabse achchhey they, aap ne aik din mujhey kisi kaam se bheja, maine kaha : Allah ki qism ! main nahi jaaunga. halanke mere dil mein ye tha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey jis kaam ka hukm diya hai main uske liye zaroor jaaunga. to main chala gaya yahan tak ke main chand ladkon ke paas se guzra, wo bazar mein khel rahe they, phir achcha (maine dekha) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne peechhey se meri guddi se mujhey pakad liya, maine aap ki taraf dekha to aap hans rahe they. aap ne farmaya : aey chhotey Anas ! kya tum wahan gaey they jahan ( janey ko) maine kaha tha? maine kaha ji haan , Allah ke rasool! mein ja raha hun."
6482,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qism maine nau (9) saal aap ki khidmat ki, maine aapko kabhi na dekha ke kisi kaam ke barey mein jo maine kya, ye kaha ho tum ne falan-falan kaam kyon kiya? aur koi cheez jo maine chhod di ho (iske barey mein kaha ho : ( tum ne falan-falan kaam kyon na kiya?"
6483,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qism maine nau (9) saal aap ki khidmat ki, maine aapko kabhi na dekha ke kisi kaam ke barey mein jo maine kya, ye kaha ho tum ne falan-falan kaam kyon kiya? aur koi cheez jo maine chhod di ho (iske barey mein kaha ho : ( tum ne falan-falan kaam kyon na kiya?"
6484,"Abu Tayyah ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tamam insanon mein sabse badh kar khush akhlaaq they."
6485,"Abu Tayyah ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tamam insanon mein sabse badh kar khush akhlaaq they."
6486,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Amr Naqid ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne ibne-Munkadir se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, kaha : aisa kabhi nahi hua ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se koi cheez mangi gaee ho aur aap ne farmaya ho : nahi."
6487,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Amr Naqid ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne ibne-Munkadir se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, kaha : aisa kabhi nahi hua ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se koi cheez mangi gaee ho aur aap ne farmaya ho : nahi."
6488,"Ashjai aur Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi donon ne Sufiyan se unhon-ne Muhammad-bin Munkadir se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they, bilkul usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah."
6489,"Ashjai aur Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi donon ne Sufiyan se unhon-ne Muhammad-bin Munkadir se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they, bilkul usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah."
6490,"Musa bin Anas ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Islam ( laney ( par jo bhi cheez talab ki jati aap wo ata farma detey, kaha : aik shakhs aap ke paas aaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 pahadon ke darmyan ( charney wali) bakriyan usey de din, wo shakhs apni qaum ki taraf wapas gaya aur kehney laga : meri qaum! musalman ho jao bila shubah Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) itna ata kartey hain ke faqr w faaqa ka andesha tak nahi rakhtey."
6491,"Musa bin Anas ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Islam ( laney ( par jo bhi cheez talab ki jati aap wo ata farma detey, kaha : aik shakhs aap ke paas aaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 pahadon ke darmyan ( charney wali) bakriyan usey de din, wo shakhs apni qaum ki taraf wapas gaya aur kehney laga : meri qaum! musalman ho jao bila shubah Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) itna ata kartey hain ke faqr w faaqa ka andesha tak nahi rakhtey."
6492,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, ke aik shakhs ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se 2 pahadon ke darmyan ( charney wali) bakriyan maangin, aap ne wo bakriyan usko ata kar din phir wo apni qaum ke paas aaya aur kehney laga : meri qaum Islam ley aao, kyonke Allah ki qasam! beshak Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) itna ata kartey hain ke faqr w faaqa ka andesha bhi nahi rakhtey. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : beshak koi aadmi sirf duniya ki talab mein bhi musalman ho jata tha, phir jiyon hi wo Islam laata tha to Islam usey duniya aur jo kuchh duniya mein hai us se badh kar mehbub ho jata tha."
6493,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, ke aik shakhs ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se 2 pahadon ke darmyan ( charney wali) bakriyan maangin, aap ne wo bakriyan usko ata kar din phir wo apni qaum ke paas aaya aur kehney laga : meri qaum Islam ley aao, kyonke Allah ki qasam! beshak Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) itna ata kartey hain ke faqr w faaqa ka andesha bhi nahi rakhtey. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : beshak koi aadmi sirf duniya ki talab mein bhi musalman ho jata tha, phir jiyon hi wo Islam laata tha to Islam usey duniya aur jo kuchh duniya mein hai us se badh kar mehbub ho jata tha."
6494,"Yunus ne mujhey ibne-Shahab se khabar di, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jange-fatah yani fateh Makka ke liye jihad kya, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un musalmanon ke sath jo aap ke sath they nikley aur Hunain mein khoonrez jang ki, Allah ne apne Deen ko aur musalmanon ko fateh ata farmai, us din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Safwan bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) ko so oont ata farmaey, phir 100 oont phir 100 oont. ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne ye bayan kya ke Safwan (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qasam! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey jo ata farmaya, so ata farmaya, mujhey tamam insanon mein sabse zyada bughz Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se tha. phir aap mujhey musalsal ata farmatey rahe yahan tak ke aap mujhey tamam insanon ki nisbat zyada mahboob ho gaey."
6495,"Yunus ne mujhey ibne-Shahab se khabar di, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jange-fatah yani fateh Makka ke liye jihad kya, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un musalmanon ke sath jo aap ke sath they nikley aur Hunain mein khoonrez jang ki, Allah ne apne Deen ko aur musalmanon ko fateh ata farmai, us din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Safwan bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) ko so oont ata farmaey, phir 100 oont phir 100 oont. ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne ye bayan kya ke Safwan (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qasam! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey jo ata farmaya, so ata farmaya, mujhey tamam insanon mein sabse zyada bughz Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se tha. phir aap mujhey musalsal ata farmatey rahe yahan tak ke aap mujhey tamam insanon ki nisbat zyada mahboob ho gaey."
6496,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Muhammad-bin Munkadir se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, (usi tarah) Sufiyan ne ibne-Munkadir se unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, neez Amr se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin Ali se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, un donon mein se har aik ne doosrey ki nisbat kuchh zayed bayan kya, isi tarah ibne-abi-Umar ne hamein hadis bayan ki, alfaz unhi ke hain. kaha : Sufiyan ne kaha : maine Muhammad-bin Munkadir se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, Sufiyan ne ye bhi kaha : maine Amr-bin-Dinar se suna, wo Muhammad-bin Ali se hadis bayan kar rahe they, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna. un donon mein se ( bhi) aik ne doosrey ki nisbat kuchh zayed bayan kya, (Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar hamarey paas Bahrain ka maal aayega to main tujhey itna, itna aur itna doonga aur donon hathon se ishara kya (yani teen lap bhar kar) . phir Bahrain ka maal aaney se pahley Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ho gaee. wo maal saiyedna Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad aaya to unhon-ne aik manaadi ko ye awaz karne ke liye hukm diya ke jiske liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh wada kya ho, ya uska qarz Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par aata ho wo aaey. ye sun kar main khada hua aur kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se wada kya tha ke agar Bahrain ka maal aayega to tujh ko itna , itna aur itna dengey. ye sun kar saiyedna Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik lap bhara phir mujh se kaha ke usko gin. maine guna to wo panch so nikley saiyedna Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke iska 2 guna aur le-ley (to teen lap ho gaey)."
6497,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Muhammad-bin Munkadir se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, (usi tarah) Sufiyan ne ibne-Munkadir se unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, neez Amr se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin Ali se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, un donon mein se har aik ne doosrey ki nisbat kuchh zayed bayan kya, isi tarah ibne-abi-Umar ne hamein hadis bayan ki, alfaz unhi ke hain. kaha : Sufiyan ne kaha : maine Muhammad-bin Munkadir se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, Sufiyan ne ye bhi kaha : maine Amr-bin-Dinar se suna, wo Muhammad-bin Ali se hadis bayan kar rahe they, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna. un donon mein se ( bhi) aik ne doosrey ki nisbat kuchh zayed bayan kya, (Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar hamarey paas Bahrain ka maal aayega to main tujhey itna, itna aur itna doonga aur donon hathon se ishara kya (yani teen lap bhar kar) . phir Bahrain ka maal aaney se pahley Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ho gaee. wo maal saiyedna Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad aaya to unhon-ne aik manaadi ko ye awaz karne ke liye hukm diya ke jiske liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh wada kya ho, ya uska qarz Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par aata ho wo aaey. ye sun kar main khada hua aur kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se wada kya tha ke agar Bahrain ka maal aayega to tujh ko itna , itna aur itna dengey. ye sun kar saiyedna Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik lap bhara phir mujh se kaha ke usko gin. maine guna to wo panch so nikley saiyedna Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke iska 2 guna aur le-ley (to teen lap ho gaey)."
6498,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey Amr-bin-Dinar ne Muhammad-bin-Ali se khabar di, unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, neez kaha : mujhey Muhammad-bin Munkadir ne (bhi) Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di thi, unhon-ne kaha : jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) faut huey to Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas (Bahrain ke governer) Hazrat Alaa bin hizrami (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf se maal aaya, Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jis shakhs ka Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par koi qarz ho ya aap ki taraf se kisi ke sath wada ho to hamarey paas aaey. ( aagey ( ibne-Uena ki hadis ki manind (tarah) ."
6499,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey Amr-bin-Dinar ne Muhammad-bin-Ali se khabar di, unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, neez kaha : mujhey Muhammad-bin Munkadir ne (bhi) Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di thi, unhon-ne kaha : jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) faut huey to Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas (Bahrain ke governer) Hazrat Alaa bin hizrami (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf se maal aaya, Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jis shakhs ka Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par koi qarz ho ya aap ki taraf se kisi ke sath wada ho to hamarey paas aaey. ( aagey ( ibne-Uena ki hadis ki manind (tarah) ."
